queryItem.expression: CASE WHEN [物理层].[R34_SQL1].[LOT_INV_STATE] = 'NonProBank' THEN CASE WHEN [物理层].[R34_SQL1].[LOT_FINISHED_STATE] IN ('SCRAPPED','EMPTIED') THEN [物理层].[R34_SQL1].[LOT_FINISHED_STATE] ELSE [物理层].[R34_SQL1].[LOT_INV_STATE] END ELSE CASE WHEN [物理层].[R34_SQL1].[LOT_HOLD_STATE] = 'ONHOLD' THEN CASE WHEN [物理层].[R34_SQL1].[LOT_FINISHED_STATE] IN ('SCRAPPED','EMPTIED') THEN [物理层].[R34_SQL1].[LOT_FINISHED_STATE] ELSE [物理层].[R34_SQL1].[LOT_HOLD_STATE] END ELSE CASE WHEN [物理层].[R34_SQL1].[LOT_STATE] IN ('LOTCREATED','RELEASED','SHIPPED') THEN [物理层].[R34_SQL1].[LOT_STATE] WHEN [物理层].[R34_SQL1].[LOT_STATE] = 'FINSIHED' THEN [物理层].[R34_SQL1].[LOT_FINISHED_STATE] WHEN [物理层].[R34_SQL1].[LOT_STATE] = 'ACTIVE' THEN [物理层].[R34_SQL1].[LOT_PROCESS_STATE] END END END

queryItem.name: Recipe Id

queryItem.name: Eqp Type
queryItem.expression: CASE WHEN [物理层].[R34_01_state3_1].[EQP_TYPE] <>'' THEN [物理层].[R34_01_state3_1].[EQP_TYPE] ELSE ( CASE WHEN [物理层].[R34_01_state3_2].[EQP_TYPE] <> '' THEN [物理层].[R34_01_state3_2].[EQP_TYPE] ELSE '' END ) END

queryItem.name: Lot Status
queryItem.expression: CASE WHEN [业务层].[REQRP041_01].[Lot Inv State] = 'NonProBank' THEN CASE WHEN [业务层].[REQRP041_01].[Lot Finished State] IN ('SCRAPPED','EMPTIED') THEN [业务层].[REQRP041_01].[Lot Finished State] ELSE [业务层].[REQRP041_01].[Lot Inv State] END ELSE CASE WHEN [业务层].[REQRP041_01].[Lot Hold State] = 'ONHOLD' THEN CASE WHEN [业务层].[REQRP041_01].[Lot Finished State] IN ('SCRAPPED','EMPTIED') THEN [业务层].[REQRP041_01].[Lot Finished State] ELSE [业务层].[REQRP041_01].[Lot Hold State] END ELSE CASE WHEN [业务层].[REQRP041_01].[Lot State] IN ('LOTCREATED','RELEASED','SHIPPED') THEN [业务层].[REQRP041_01].[Lot State] WHEN [业务层].[REQRP041_01].[Lot State] = 'FINSIHED' THEN [业务层].[REQRP041_01].[Lot Finished State] WHEN [业务层].[REQRP041_01].[Lot State] = 'ACTIVE' THEN [业务层].[REQRP041_01].[Lot Process State] END END END

dbQuery.sql: SELECT TEMP1.*,TEMP2.PRODSPEC_ID AS PRODSPEC_ID1 FROM (SELECT T1.OPE_NO, T1.OPE_NAME, T1.D_THESYSTEMKEY, W.WIP_QTY, W.INPROCESS_QTY, W.LOTRESERVED_QTY, W.WAIT4RESERVED_QTY, W.HOLD_QTY, W.FUTUREHOLD_QTY, W.PRODSPEC_ID, W.MAINPD_ID FROM ( SELECT PO.OPER_NO AS OPE_NO, PD.PD_NAME AS OPE_NAME, PO.D_THESYSTEMKEY FROM SMVIEW.FBMNPD_PO_M PO, SMVIEW.FBPD_M PD WHERE PD.D_THESYSTEMKEY=PO.PD_IDENT )T1 LEFT JOIN ( SELECT OPE_NO, PRODSPEC_ID, MAINPD_ID, SUM(WIP_QTY) AS WIP_QTY, SUM(INPROCESS_QTY) AS INPROCESS_QTY, SUM(LOTRESERVED_QTY) AS LOTRESERVED_QTY, SUM(WAIT4RESERVED_QTY) AS WAIT4RESERVED_QTY, SUM(HOLD_QTY) AS HOLD_QTY, SUM(FUTUREHOLD_QTY) AS FUTUREHOLD_QTY FROM ( SELECT L.OPE_NO , L.QTY AS WIP_QTY , CASE WHEN LOT_HOLD_STATE <> 'ONHOLD' THEN CASE WHEN LOT_PROCESS_STATE = 'Processing' THEN QTY ELSE NULL END END AS INPROCESS_QTY , CASE WHEN LOT_HOLD_STATE <> 'ONHOLD' THEN CASE WHEN LOT_PROCESS_STATE = 'Waiting' THEN CASE WHEN CTRLJOB_ID<>'' THEN QTY ELSE NULL END END END AS LOTRESERVED_QTY , CASE WHEN LOT_HOLD_STATE <> 'ONHOLD' THEN CASE WHEN LOT_PROCESS_STATE = 'Waiting' THEN CASE WHEN CTRLJOB_ID='' THEN QTY ELSE NULL END END END AS WAIT4RESERVED_QTY , CASE WHEN H.HOLD_QTY > 0 THEN QTY ELSE NULL END AS HOLD_QTY , CASE WHEN H.FUTUREHOLD_QTY > 0 THEN QTY ELSE NULL END AS FUTUREHOLD_QTY ,L.PRODSPEC_ID ,L.MAINPD_ID FROM MMVIEW.FRLOT L LEFT JOIN( SELECT D_THESYSTEMKEY, SUM( CASE WHEN HOLD_TYPE IN ('FutureHold','MergeHold','WaitingMonitorHold') THEN 1 ELSE NULL END ) AS FUTUREHOLD_QTY, SUM( CASE WHEN HOLD_TYPE IN ('LotHold','BankHold','MonitorSPCHold','MonitorSpecHod','ReworkHold','SPCOutOfRangeHold','SpecOverHold','ProcessHold','RecipeHold') THEN 1 ELSE NULL END ) AS HOLD_QTY FROM MMVIEW.FRLOT_HOLDRECORD GROUP BY D_THESYSTEMKEY )H ON H.D_THESYSTEMKEY=L.D_THESYSTEMKEY WHERE L.LOT_TYPE IN ('Production','Engineering') AND L.LOT_STATE='ACTIVE' AND L.LOT_INV_STATE='OnFloor' AND L.LOT_FINISHED_STATE='' AND L.LOT_PROCESS_STATE<>'Processed' )WIP1 GROUP BY OPE_NO,PRODSPEC_ID,MAINPD_ID ) W ON W.OPE_NO=T1.OPE_NO ORDER BY T1.OPE_NO) TEMP1, (SELECT PRODSPEC_ID, MAINPD_ID FROM mmview.FRPRODSPEC WHERE PROD_CATEGORY_ID IN ('Production','Engineering') ORDER BY PRODSPEC_ID) TEMP2 WHERE TEMP1.D_THESYSTEMKEY=TEMP2.MAINPD_ID AND TEMP1.MAINPD_ID=TEMP2.MAINPD_ID AND TEMP1.PRODSPEC_ID=TEMP2.PRODSPEC_ID

SELECT PRODSPEC_ID, MAINPD_ID, OPE_NO, OPE_NAME, LOT_ID, LOT_STATE, LOT_HOLD_STATE AS LOT_STATUS, QTY FROM MMVIEW.FRLOT L, ( SELECT D_THESYSTEMKEY, SUM( CASE WHEN HOLD_TYPE IN ('FutureHold','MergeHold','WaitingMonitorHold') THEN 1 ELSE NULL END ) AS FUTUREHOLD_QTY, SUM( CASE WHEN HOLD_TYPE IN ('LotHold','BankHold','MonitorSPCHold','MonitorSpecHod','ReworkHold','SPCOutOfRangeHold','SpecOverHold','ProcessHold','RecipeHold') THEN 1 ELSE NULL END ) AS HOLD_QTY FROM MMVIEW.FRLOT_HOLDRECORD GROUP BY D_THESYSTEMKEY )H WHERE LOT_TYPE IN ('Production','Engineering') AND LOT_STATE='ACTIVE' AND LOT_INV_STATE='OnFloor' AND LOT_FINISHED_STATE='' AND LOT_PROCESS_STATE<>'Processed' AND LOT_HOLD_STATE='ONHOLD' AND H.D_THESYSTEMKEY=L.D_THESYSTEMKEY AND H.HOLD_QTY IS NOT NULL ORDER BY LOT_ID

SELECT PRODSPEC_ID, MAINPD_ID, OPE_NO, OPE_NAME, LOT_ID, LOT_STATE, CASE WHEN LOT_INV_STATE = 'NonProBank' THEN CASE WHEN LOT_FINISHED_STATE IN ('SCRAPPED','EMPTIED') THEN LOT_FINISHED_STATE ELSE LOT_INV_STATE END ELSE CASE WHEN LOT_HOLD_STATE = 'ONHOLD' THEN CASE WHEN LOT_FINISHED_STATE IN ('SCRAPPED','EMPTIED') THEN LOT_FINISHED_STATE ELSE LOT_HOLD_STATE END ELSE CASE WHEN LOT_STATE IN ('LOTCREATED','RELEASED','SHIPPED') THEN LOT_STATE WHEN LOT_STATE = 'FINSIHED' THEN LOT_FINISHED_STATE WHEN LOT_STATE = 'ACTIVE' THEN LOT_PROCESS_STATE END END END AS LOT_STATUS, QTY FROM MMVIEW.FRLOT WHERE LOT_TYPE IN ('Production','Engineering') AND LOT_STATE='ACTIVE' AND LOT_INV_STATE='OnFloor' AND LOT_FINISHED_STATE='' AND LOT_PROCESS_STATE<>'Processed' ORDER BY LOT_ID

SELECT PRODSPEC_ID, MAINPD_ID, OPE_NO, OPE_NAME, LOT_ID, LOT_STATE, CASE WHEN LOT_INV_STATE = 'NonProBank' THEN CASE WHEN LOT_FINISHED_STATE IN ('SCRAPPED','EMPTIED') THEN LOT_FINISHED_STATE ELSE LOT_INV_STATE END ELSE CASE WHEN LOT_HOLD_STATE = 'ONHOLD' THEN CASE WHEN LOT_FINISHED_STATE IN ('SCRAPPED','EMPTIED') THEN LOT_FINISHED_STATE ELSE LOT_HOLD_STATE END ELSE CASE WHEN LOT_STATE IN ('LOTCREATED','RELEASED','SHIPPED') THEN LOT_STATE WHEN LOT_STATE = 'FINSIHED' THEN LOT_FINISHED_STATE WHEN LOT_STATE = 'ACTIVE' THEN LOT_PROCESS_STATE END END END AS LOT_STATUS, QTY FROM MMVIEW.FRLOT WHERE LOT_TYPE IN ('Production','Engineering') AND LOT_STATE='ACTIVE' AND LOT_INV_STATE='OnFloor' AND LOT_FINISHED_STATE='' AND LOT_PROCESS_STATE<>'Processed' AND LOT_HOLD_STATE='NOTONHOLD' AND LOT_PROCESS_STATE='Processing' ORDER BY LOT_ID

SELECT PRODSPEC_ID, MAINPD_ID, OPE_NO, OPE_NAME, LOT_ID, LOT_STATE, CASE WHEN LOT_INV_STATE = 'NonProBank' THEN CASE WHEN LOT_FINISHED_STATE IN ('SCRAPPED','EMPTIED') THEN LOT_FINISHED_STATE ELSE LOT_INV_STATE END ELSE CASE WHEN LOT_HOLD_STATE = 'ONHOLD' THEN CASE WHEN LOT_FINISHED_STATE IN ('SCRAPPED','EMPTIED') THEN LOT_FINISHED_STATE ELSE LOT_HOLD_STATE END ELSE CASE WHEN LOT_STATE IN ('LOTCREATED','RELEASED','SHIPPED') THEN LOT_STATE WHEN LOT_STATE = 'FINSIHED' THEN LOT_FINISHED_STATE WHEN LOT_STATE = 'ACTIVE' THEN LOT_PROCESS_STATE END END END AS LOT_STATUS, QTY FROM MMVIEW.FRLOT WHERE LOT_TYPE IN ('Production','Engineering') AND LOT_STATE='ACTIVE' AND LOT_INV_STATE='OnFloor' AND LOT_FINISHED_STATE='' AND LOT_PROCESS_STATE<>'Processed' AND LOT_HOLD_STATE='NOTONHOLD’' AND LOT_PROCESS_STATE='Waiting' AND CTRLJOB_ID<> '' ORDER BY LOT_ID

SELECT PRODSPEC_ID, MAINPD_ID, OPE_NO, OPE_NAME, LOT_ID, LOT_STATE, CASE WHEN LOT_INV_STATE = 'NonProBank' THEN CASE WHEN LOT_FINISHED_STATE IN ('SCRAPPED','EMPTIED') THEN LOT_FINISHED_STATE ELSE LOT_INV_STATE END ELSE CASE WHEN LOT_HOLD_STATE = 'ONHOLD' THEN CASE WHEN LOT_FINISHED_STATE IN ('SCRAPPED','EMPTIED') THEN LOT_FINISHED_STATE ELSE LOT_HOLD_STATE END ELSE CASE WHEN LOT_STATE IN ('LOTCREATED','RELEASED','SHIPPED') THEN LOT_STATE WHEN LOT_STATE = 'FINSIHED' THEN LOT_FINISHED_STATE WHEN LOT_STATE = 'ACTIVE' THEN LOT_PROCESS_STATE END END END AS LOT_STATUS, QTY FROM MMVIEW.FRLOT WHERE LOT_TYPE IN ('Production','Engineering') AND LOT_STATE='ACTIVE' AND LOT_INV_STATE='OnFloor' AND LOT_FINISHED_STATE='' AND LOT_PROCESS_STATE<>'Processed' AND LOT_HOLD_STATE='NOTONHOLD' AND LOT_PROCESS_STATE='Waiting' AND CTRLJOB_ID= '' ORDER BY LOT_ID

SELECT PRODSPEC_ID, MAINPD_ID, OPE_NO, OPE_NAME, LOT_ID, LOT_STATE, LOT_HOLD_STATE AS LOT_STATUS, QTY FROM MMVIEW.FRLOT L, ( SELECT D_THESYSTEMKEY, SUM( CASE WHEN HOLD_TYPE IN ('FutureHold','MergeHold','WaitingMonitorHold') THEN 1 ELSE NULL END ) AS FUTUREHOLD_QTY, SUM( CASE WHEN HOLD_TYPE IN ('LotHold','BankHold','MonitorSPCHold','MonitorSpecHod','ReworkHold','SPCOutOfRangeHold','SpecOverHold','ProcessHold','RecipeHold') THEN 1 ELSE NULL END ) AS HOLD_QTY FROM MMVIEW.FRLOT_HOLDRECORD GROUP BY D_THESYSTEMKEY )H WHERE LOT_TYPE IN ('Production','Engineering') AND LOT_STATE='ACTIVE' AND LOT_INV_STATE='OnFloor' AND LOT_FINISHED_STATE='' AND LOT_PROCESS_STATE<>'Processed' AND LOT_HOLD_STATE='ONHOLD' AND H.D_THESYSTEMKEY=L.D_THESYSTEMKEY AND H.FUTUREHOLD_QTY IS NOT NULL ORDER BY LOT_ID

SELECT a.EQP_ID,s.STK_ID, s.STK_NAME, s.E10_STATE, s.CUR_STATE_ID, a.CAST_ID, a.value FROM MMVIEW.FRSTK s LEFT JOIN ( SELECT c.EQP_ID,c.CAST_ID, c.EQP_OBJ, u.VALUE FROM MMVIEW.FRCAST c JOIN MMVIEW.FRCAST_UDATA u ON c.D_THESYSTEMKEY = u.D_THESYSTEMKEY WHERE c.TRANS_STATE = 'MI' AND u.name = 'CAST_LOCATION' ) a ON a.EQP_OBJ = s.STK_OBJ ORDER BY s.STK_ID, a.CAST_ID
select CURRENT_TIMESTAMP AS CURRENT_TIME,SUB_LOT_TYPE, LEADING_CHAR from MMVIEW.FRLOTTYPE LOTTYPE,MMVIEW.FRLOTTYPE_SUBTYPE SUBLOTTYPE where LOTTYPE.D_THESYSTEMKEY=SUBLOTTYPE.D_THESYSTEMKEY
Select * from ISTRPT.RPTWFRSTART_SUM RPTWFRSTART_SUM

SELECT OPE1.LOT_ID, OPE1.LOT_TYPE, OPE1.CUR_WAFER_QTY, OPE1.CLAIM_USER_ID AS HOLD_USER, OPE1.CLAIM_TIME AS HOLD_TIME, OPE2.CLAIM_TIME AS RELEASE_TIME, CASE WHEN OPE2.CLAIM_TIME IS NULL THEN DECIMAL(DOUBLE(TIMESTAMPDIFF(4, CURRENT TIMESTAMP-OPE1.CLAIM_TIME))/60, 6, 2) ELSE DECIMAL(DOUBLE(TIMESTAMPDIFF(4, OPE2.CLAIM_TIME -OPE1.CLAIM_TIME))/60, 6, 2) END AS DURATION, OPE1.REASON_CODE, OPE1.CLAIM_MEMO AS HOLD_COMMENT, OPE2.CLAIM_USER_ID AS RELEASE_USER, SUBSTR(OPE2.CLAIM_MEMO,1,64) AS RELEASE_COMMENT, OPE1.HOLD_REASON_OPE_NO, OPE1.MODULEPD_ID, ope1.department FROM (
SELECT T1.LOT_ID, T1.LOT_TYPE, T1.CUR_WAFER_QTY, T1.CLAIM_USER_ID, T1.CLAIM_TIME, T1.REASON_CODE, T1.HOLD_REASON_OPE_NO, T1.CLAIM_MEMO, T1.HOLD_REASON_MAINPD_ID, T1.HOLD_REASON_PD_ID, T1.HOLD_TYPE, SMPO.MODPD_IDENT AS MODULEPD_ID, pd.department from ( SELECT LOT_ID, LOT_TYPE, CUR_WAFER_QTY, CLAIM_USER_ID, CLAIM_TIME, REASON_CODE, HOLD_REASON_OPE_NO, SUBSTR(CLAIM_MEMO,1,64) AS CLAIM_MEMO , CASE WHEN OPE.HOLD_REASON_OPE_NO=OPE.OPE_NO THEN OPE.MAINPD_ID ELSE OPE.PREV_MAINPD_ID END AS HOLD_REASON_MAINPD_ID, CASE WHEN OPE.HOLD_REASON_OPE_NO=OPE.OPE_NO THEN OPE.PD_ID ELSE OPE.PREV_PD_ID END AS HOLD_REASON_PD_ID, HOLD_TYPE FROM mmview.FHOPEHS OPE WHERE OPE_CATEGORY='LotHold' ) T1 left join SMVIEW.FBMNPD_po_m SMPO on SMPO.D_THESYSTEMKEY=T1.HOLD_REASON_MAINPD_ID AND SMPO.oper_no =T1.HOLD_REASON_OPE_NO left join mmview.frpd pd on T1.HOLD_REASON_PD_ID =PD.PD_ID AND PD.PD_LEVEL='Operation' ) OPE1 LEFT JOIN mmview.FHOPEHS OPE2 ON OPE1.LOT_ID=OPE2.LOT_ID AND OPE1.REASON_CODE=OPE2.HOLD_REASON_CODE AND OPE1.CLAIM_TIME=OPE2.HOLD_TIME AND OPE1.HOLD_REASON_OPE_NO=OPE2.HOLD_REASON_OPE_NO AND OPE1.HOLD_TYPE=OPE2.HOLD_TYPE AND OPE2.OPE_CATEGORY='LotHoldRelease' ORDER BY OPE1.LOT_ID, HOLD_TIME

SELECT OPE1.DEPARTMENT, OPE1.LOT_ID, OPE1.LOT_TYPE, OPE1.CLAIM_TIME AS HOLD_TIME, OPE1.REASON_CODE AS HOLD_CODE, OPE1.CUR_WAFER_QTY AS QTY, OPE1.CLAIM_MEMO AS HOLD_COMMENT, OPE2.CLAIM_TIME AS RELEASE_TIME, CURRENT_TIMESTAMP AS CURRENT_TIME FROM ( SELECT LOT_ID, LOT_TYPE, CLAIM_TIME, REASON_CODE, CUR_WAFER_QTY, CLAIM_MEMO, HOLD_REASON_OPE_NO, HOLD_TYPE, PD.DEPARTMENT FROM ( SELECT LOT_ID, LOT_TYPE, CLAIM_TIME, REASON_CODE, CUR_WAFER_QTY, SUBSTR(CLAIM_MEMO,1,64) AS CLAIM_MEMO, HOLD_REASON_OPE_NO, CASE WHEN OPE.HOLD_REASON_OPE_NO=OPE.OPE_NO THEN OPE.PD_ID ELSE OPE.PREV_PD_ID END AS HOLD_REASON_PD_ID, HOLD_TYPE FROM MMVIEW.FHOPEHS OPE WHERE OPE_CATEGORY='LotHold' )T1,MMVIEW.FRPD PD WHERE T1.HOLD_REASON_PD_ID =PD.PD_ID AND PD.PD_LEVEL='Operation' )OPE1 LEFT JOIN MMVIEW.FHOPEHS OPE2 ON OPE1.LOT_ID=OPE2.LOT_ID AND OPE1.REASON_CODE=OPE2.HOLD_REASON_CODE AND OPE1.CLAIM_TIME=OPE2.HOLD_TIME AND OPE1.HOLD_REASON_OPE_NO = OPE2.HOLD_REASON_OPE_NO AND OPE1.HOLD_TYPE = OPE2.HOLD_TYPE AND OPE2.OPE_CATEGORY='LotHoldRelease' ORDER BY OPE1.LOT_ID,HOLD_TIME

SELECT LOT_ID, LOT_OWNER_ID, LOT_TYPE, SCRAPTYPE, CLAIM_TIME, CASE WHEN REASON_MAINPD_ID <>'' AND REASON_OPE_NO <> '' THEN EVENTTIME2 ELSE EVENTTIME END AS EVENTTIME, PRODSPEC_ID, QTY, MODPD_IDENT, REASON_OPE_NO, CASE WHEN REASON_MAINPD_ID <>'' AND REASON_OPE_NO <> '' AND REASON_EQP_ID2 IS NOT NULL THEN REASON_EQP_ID2 ELSE REASON_EQP_ID END AS REASON_EQP_ID, CASE WHEN REASON_MAINPD_ID <>'' AND REASON_OPE_NO <> '' AND REASON_USER_ID2 IS NOT NULL THEN REASON_USER_ID2 ELSE REASON_USER_ID END AS REASON_USER_ID, REASON_CODE, REASON_DESCRIPTION, REASON_MAINPD_ID, DEPARTMENT, LOT_FAMILY_ID, PREV_LOT_ID, CURRENT_TIMESTAMP AS CURRENT_TIME FROM ( SELECT ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY T2.LOT_ID,T2.LOT_OWNER_ID,T2.LOT_TYPE,T2.SCRAPTYPE, T2.CLAIM_TIME,T2.EVENTTIME, T2.PRODSPEC_ID, T2.QTY,T2.MODPD_IDENT, T2.REASON_OPE_NO, T2.REASON_EQP_ID, T2.REASON_USER_ID, T2.REASON_CODE, T2.REASON_DESCRIPTION,T2.REASON_MAINPD_ID ORDER BY T3.EVENTTIME DESC) AS ROW_COL, T2.LOT_ID AS LOT_ID, T2.LOT_OWNER_ID, T2.LOT_TYPE,T2.SCRAPTYPE, T2.CLAIM_TIME, T2.EVENTTIME, T2.PRODSPEC_ID, T2.QTY, T2.MODPD_IDENT, T2.REASON_OPE_NO, T2.REASON_EQP_ID, T2.REASON_USER_ID, T2.REASON_CODE, T2.REASON_DESCRIPTION, T2.REASON_MAINPD_ID, T3.EVENTTIME AS EVENTTIME2, T3.REASON_EQP_ID AS REASON_EQP_ID2 , T3.REASON_USER_ID AS REASON_USER_ID2, T4.DEPARTMENT, T5.LOT_FAMILY_ID, T6.PREV_LOT_ID FROM ( SELECT T1.LOT_ID, T1.LOT_OWNER_ID, T1.LOT_TYPE, T1.SCRAPTYPE, T1.CLAIM_TIME, '' AS EVENTTIME, T1.PRODSPEC_ID, T1.QTY, SMPO.MODPD_IDENT, T1.REASON_OPE_NO, '' AS REASON_EQP_ID, '' AS REASON_USER_ID, T1.REASON_CODE, T1.REASON_DESCRIPTION, T1.REASON_MAINPD_ID FROM ( SELECT LOT_ID, LOT_OWNER_ID, LOT_TYPE, PRODSPEC_ID, REASON_MAINPD_ID, REASON_OPE_NO, REASON_CODE, REASON_DESCRIPTION, CASE SCRAP_TYPE WHEN 'WS' THEN 'WaferScrap' WHEN 'WC' THEN 'WaferScrapCancel' WHEN 'CS' THEN 'ChipScrap' WHEN 'CC' THEN 'ChipScrapCancel' ELSE '' END AS SCRAPTYPE, CLAIM_TIME, CASE WHEN SCRAP_TYPE IN ('WS', 'CS') THEN SUM(SCRAP_UNIT_COUNT) WHEN SCRAP_TYPE IN ('WC', 'CC') THEN SUM(SCRAP_UNIT_COUNT)*-1 ELSE 0 END AS QTY FROM MMVIEW.FHSCRHS GROUP BY LOT_ID, LOT_OWNER_ID, LOT_TYPE, PRODSPEC_ID, REASON_MAINPD_ID, REASON_OPE_NO, REASON_CODE, REASON_DESCRIPTION,SCRAP_TYPE,CLAIM_TIME )T1, SMVIEW.FBMNPD_PO SMPO WHERE T1.REASON_MAINPD_ID=SMPO.D_THESYSTEMKEY AND T1.REASON_OPE_NO=SMPO.OPER_NO ORDER BY LOT_ID, CLAIM_TIME )T2 LEFT JOIN ( SELECT LOT_ID, PREV_MAINPD_ID, PREV_OPE_NO, CLAIM_TIME AS EVENTTIME, EQP_ID AS REASON_EQP_ID, CLAIM_USER_ID AS REASON_USER_ID FROM MMVIEW.FHOPEHS WHERE OPE_CATEGORY='OperationComplete' ) T3 ON T2.LOT_ID=T3.LOT_ID AND T2.REASON_OPE_NO=T3.PREV_OPE_NO AND T3.EVENTTIME<T2.CLAIM_TIME LEFT JOIN ( SELECT DEPARTMENT,USER_ID FROM MMVIEW.FRUSER ) T4 ON T2.LOT_OWNER_ID = T4.USER_ID LEFT JOIN ( SELECT LOT_ID,LOT_FAMILY_ID FROM MMVIEW.FRLOT ) T5 ON T2.LOT_ID = T5.LOT_ID LEFT JOIN ( SELECT * FROM ( SELECT ROW_NUMBER() OVER(Partition by CUR_LOT_ID,PREV_LOT_ID ) AS ROW_COL1, OPE_CATEGORY,CUR_LOT_ID,PREV_LOT_ID FROM MMVIEW.FHWLTHS a WHERE OPE_CATEGORY='STB' ) WHERE ROW_COL1 = 1 )T6 ON T5.LOT_FAMILY_ID = T6.CUR_LOT_ID ORDER BY LOT_ID, CLAIM_TIME ) WHERE ROW_COL=1

SELECT T1.PROD,T2.* FROM (SELECT distinct(rtrim(CHAR(SUBTYPE.LEADING_CHAR||SUBSTR(PUDATA.VALUE,4)))) AS PROD, P.MAINPD_OBJ
FROM MMVIEW.FRLOTTYPE LOTTYPE , MMVIEW.FRLOTTYPE_SUBTYPE SUBTYPE , MMVIEW.FRPRODSPEC P , MMVIEW.FRPRODSPEC_UDATA PUDATA , MMVIEW.FRPD PD WHERE LOTTYPE.LOTTYPE_ID='Production' AND LOTTYPE.D_THESYSTEMKEY=SUBTYPE.D_THESYSTEMKEY AND P.PROD_CATEGORY_ID='Production' AND P.D_THESYSTEMKEY=PUDATA.D_THESYSTEMKEY AND PUDATA.NAME='S_PROD_LotIDSubLeading' AND PUDATA.VALUE<>'' AND P.MAINPD_OBJ=PD.PD_OBJ ORDER BY PROD,P.MAINPD_OBJ)T1 , (SELECT PDLIST.D_KEY, PDLIST.PD_ID AS MODULEPD_ID, PD.PD_OBJ, DECIMAL(SUM(PD2.STD_CYCLE_TIME)/60, 10, 2) AS CT_HRS, 0 AS MODULE_MOVE_LOT_QTY, 0 AS HOLD_LOT_QTY, 0 AS SUPERHOT_LOT_QTY, 0 AS HOT_LOT_QTY, 0 AS URGENT_LOT_QTY, 0 AS PRODUCT_LOT_QTY, 0 AS PRODUCT_WAFER_QTY, 0 AS ACCU_WIP_WAFER_QTY, 0 AS WIP_REQ_WAFER_QTY, CURRENT_TIMESTAMP AS CURRENT_TIME FROM MMVIEW.FRPD PD , MMVIEW.FRPF PF , MMVIEW.FRPF_PDLIST PDLIST , MMVIEW.FRPD PD1 , MMVIEW.FRPF PF1 , MMVIEW.FRPF_POSLIST POSLIST , MMVIEW.FRPOS POS , MMVIEW.FRPD PD2
WHERE PD.ACTIVE_MAINPF_OBJ=PF.PF_OBJ AND PF.D_THESYSTEMKEY=PDLIST.D_THESYSTEMKEY AND PDLIST.PD_OBJ=PD1.PD_OBJ AND PD1.ACTIVE_PF_OBJ=PF1.PF_OBJ AND PF1.D_THESYSTEMKEY=POSLIST.D_THESYSTEMKEY AND POSLIST.POS_OBJ=POS.POS_OBJ AND POS.PD_OBJ=PD2.PD_OBJ GROUP BY PDLIST.D_KEY, PDLIST.PD_ID,PD.PD_OBJ ORDER BY PDLIST.D_KEY)T2 WHERE T1.MAINPD_OBJ=T2.PD_OBJ

select MODULEPD_ID,TABLE_NAME,LOT_ID,SNAP_TIME,LOT_INV_STATE,count(*) AS LOT_QTY,sum(QTY) AS WAFER_QTY FROM (select * from (SELECT MODULEPD_ID, QTY, LOT.LOT_ID, SNAP_TIME AS SNAP_TIME, LOT_INV_STATE, 'RPT_LOT_SNAPSHOT' TABLE_NAME FROM ISTRPT.RPT_LOT_SNAPSHOT LOT, MMVIEW.FRLOTPO PO WHERE LOT_HOLD_STATE='ONHOLD' AND PRIORITY_CLASS=5 AND LOT.LOT_ID=PO.LOT_ID)
UNION select * from (SELECT MODULEPD_ID, QTY, LOT.LOT_ID, to_date(to_char(current timestamp,'yyyy-mm-dd hh24'),'yyyy-mm-dd hh24') AS SNAP_TIME, LOT_INV_STATE, 'FRLOT' TABLE_NAME FROM MMVIEW.FRLOT LOT, MMVIEW.FRLOTPO PO WHERE LOT_HOLD_STATE='ONHOLD' AND PRIORITY_CLASS=5 AND LOT.LOT_ID=PO.LOT_ID) ) GROUP BY MODULEPD_ID,TABLE_NAME,LOT_ID,SNAP_TIME,LOT_INV_STATE ORDER BY MODULEPD_ID,TABLE_NAME

select MODULEPD_ID,TABLE_NAME,LOT_ID,SNAP_TIME,LOT_INV_STATE,count(*) AS LOT_QTY,sum(QTY) AS WAFER_QTY FROM (select * from (SELECT MODULEPD_ID, QTY, LOT.LOT_ID, SNAP_TIME AS SNAP_TIME, LOT_INV_STATE, 'RPT_LOT_SNAPSHOT' TABLE_NAME FROM ISTRPT.RPT_LOT_SNAPSHOT LOT, MMVIEW.FRLOTPO PO WHERE LOT_HOLD_STATE='ONHOLD' AND PRIORITY_CLASS=4 AND LOT.LOT_ID=PO.LOT_ID)
UNION select * from (SELECT MODULEPD_ID, QTY, LOT.LOT_ID, to_date(to_char(current timestamp,'yyyy-mm-dd hh24'),'yyyy-mm-dd hh24') AS SNAP_TIME, LOT_INV_STATE, 'FRLOT' TABLE_NAME FROM MMVIEW.FRLOT LOT, MMVIEW.FRLOTPO PO WHERE LOT_HOLD_STATE='ONHOLD' AND PRIORITY_CLASS=4 AND LOT.LOT_ID=PO.LOT_ID) ) GROUP BY MODULEPD_ID,TABLE_NAME,LOT_ID,SNAP_TIME,LOT_INV_STATE ORDER BY MODULEPD_ID,TABLE_NAME

UNION select * from (SELECT MODULEPD_ID, QTY, LOT.LOT_ID, to_date(to_char(current timestamp,'yyyy-mm-dd hh24'),'yyyy-mm-dd hh24') AS SNAP_TIME, LOT_INV_STATE, 'FRLOT' TABLE_NAME FROM MMVIEW.FRLOT LOT, MMVIEW.FRLOTPO PO WHERE LOT.LOT_ID=PO.LOT_ID) ) GROUP BY MODULEPD_ID,TABLE_NAME,LOT_ID,SNAP_TIME,LOT_INV_STATE ORDER BY MODULEPD_ID,TABLE_NAME

select T1.LOT_ID, T1.OPE_CATEGORY, T1.LOT_TYPE, T1.CLAIM_TIME, T1.CUR_WAFER_QTY, T1.OPE_NO, PO.MODPD_IDENT AS MODULEPD_ID, T1.PD_NAME, T1.CLAIM_USER_ID, T1.EQP_ID, T1.RECIPE_ID, T1.RETICLE_ID, T1.REASON_CODE, T1.REASON_DESCRIPTION, T1.CAST_ID, T1.PRODSPEC_ID, CURRENT_TIMESTAMP AS CURRENT_TIME from ( SELECT OPE.LOT_ID, OPE.OPE_CATEGORY, OPE.LOT_TYPE, OPE.CLAIM_TIME, OPE.CUR_WAFER_QTY, CASE OPE.OPE_CATEGORY WHEN 'OperationComplete' THEN OPE.PREV_OPE_NO ELSE OPE.OPE_NO END AS OPE_NO, CASE OPE.OPE_CATEGORY WHEN 'OperationComplete' THEN OPE.PREV_PD_NAME ELSE OPE.PD_NAME END AS PD_NAME, OPE.CLAIM_USER_ID, OPE.EQP_ID, OPE.RECIPE_ID, RETICLE.RETICLE_ID, OPE.REASON_CODE, OPE.REASON_DESCRIPTION, OPE.CAST_ID, OPE.PRODSPEC_ID, CASE OPE.OPE_CATEGORY WHEN 'OperationComplete' THEN OPE.PREV_MAINPD_ID ELSE OPE.MAINPD_ID END AS MAINPD_ID
FROM MMVIEW.FHOPEHS OPE LEFT JOIN MMVIEW.FHOPEHS_RETICLE RETICLE ON OPE.LOT_ID=RETICLE.LOT_ID AND OPE.MAINPD_ID=RETICLE.MAINPD_ID AND OPE.OPE_NO=RETICLE.OPE_NO AND OPE.OPE_PASS_COUNT=RETICLE.OPE_PASS_COUNT AND OPE.CLAIM_TIME=RETICLE.CLAIM_TIME AND OPE.OPE_CATEGORY=RETICLE.OPE_CATEGORY AND OPE.OPE_CATEGORY='OperationStart' WHERE NOT (OPE.OPE_CATEGORY='LocateForward' AND MOVE_TYPE='BackwardOperation') AND NOT (OPE.OPE_CATEGORY='LocateBackward' AND MOVE_TYPE='ForwardOperation' ) AND NOT (OPE.OPE_CATEGORY='Branch' AND MOVE_TYPE='BackwardOperation') AND NOT (OPE.OPE_CATEGORY='BranchCancel' AND MOVE_TYPE='ForwardOperation' ) AND NOT (OPE.OPE_CATEGORY='Rework' AND MOVE_TYPE='BackwardOperation') AND NOT (OPE.OPE_CATEGORY='ReworkCancel' AND MOVE_TYPE='ForwardOperation' ) AND NOT (OPE.OPE_CATEGORY='ScheduleChange' AND (MOVE_TYPE='BackwardStage' OR MOVE_TYPE='NonMove' ))) as T1, SMVIEW.FBMNPD_PO PO WHERE PO.D_THESYSTEMKEY=T1.MAINPD_ID AND PO.OPER_NO=T1.OPE_NO ORDER BY T1.CLAIM_TIME

WITH T1 AS ( SELECT OPE.LOT_TYPE, OPE.CUR_WAFER_QTY, SMPO.MODPD_IDENT, OPE.OPE_NO, OPE.PD_NAME, DEPT.DESC AS DEPARTMENT, EQP.EQP_TYPE, DECIMAL((PD. STD_PROC_TIME+PD. STD_WAIT_TIME)/60 ,10,2) AS CT_HRS, OPE.CLAIM_TIME AS OPESTART_TIME, OPE.MAINPD_ID, OPE.OPE_PASS_COUNT, OPE.LOT_ID FROM MMVIEW.FHOPEHS OPE , SMVIEW.FBMNPD_PO SMPO , SMVIEW.FBPD PD , SMVIEW.FBDEPT DEPT , MMVIEW.FREQP EQP WHERE OPE.OPE_CATEGORY='OperationStart' AND SMPO.D_THESYSTEMKEY=OPE.MAINPD_ID AND SMPO.PD_IDENT=OPE.PD_ID AND OPE.PD_ID=PD.D_THESYSTEMKEY AND PD.DEPT_OBJREF=DEPT.D_STRINGOBJREF AND OPE.EQP_ID=EQP.EQP_ID ORDER BY OPE.CLAIM_TIME) , T2 AS ( SELECT T1.LOT_TYPE, T1.CUR_WAFER_QTY, T1.MODPD_IDENT, T1.OPE_NO, T1.PD_NAME, T1.DEPARTMENT, T1.EQP_TYPE, T1.CT_HRS, T1.OPESTART_TIME, T1.MAINPD_ID, T1.OPE_PASS_COUNT, T1.LOT_ID, OPE2.CLAIM_TIME AS CANCEL_TIME FROM T1 LEFT JOIN MMVIEW.FHOPEHS OPE2 ON OPE2.LOT_ID=T1.LOT_ID AND OPE2.MAINPD_ID=T1.MAINPD_ID AND OPE2.OPE_NO=T1.OPE_NO AND OPE2.OPE_PASS_COUNT=T1.OPE_PASS_COUNT AND OPE2.OPE_CATEGORY='OperationStartCancel' AND OPE2.CLAIM_TIME > T1.OPESTART_TIME ) , T3 AS ( SELECT T2.LOT_TYPE, T2.CUR_WAFER_QTY, T2.MODPD_IDENT, T2.OPE_NO, T2.PD_NAME, T2.DEPARTMENT, T2.EQP_TYPE, T2.CT_HRS, T2.OPESTART_TIME, T2.MAINPD_ID, T2.OPE_PASS_COUNT, T2.LOT_ID, CASE WHEN T2.CANCEL_TIME IS NOT NULL THEN T2.CANCEL_TIME ELSE OPE3.CLAIM_TIME END AS OPEOUT_TIME FROM T2 LEFT JOIN MMVIEW.FHOPEHS OPE3 ON OPE3.LOT_ID=T2.LOT_ID AND OPE3.PREV_MAINPD_ID=T2.MAINPD_ID AND OPE3.PREV_OPE_NO=T2.OPE_NO AND OPE3.PREV_PASS_COUNT=T2.OPE_PASS_COUNT AND OPE3.OPE_CATEGORY='OperationComplete' AND OPE3.CLAIM_TIME > T2.OPESTART_TIME ) , T4 AS ( SELECT * FROM (SELECT ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY OPE4.MAINPD_ID,OPE4.OPE_NO,OPE4.OPE_PASS_COUNT ORDER BY OPE4.CLAIM_TIME) AS ROW_COL, OPE4.MAINPD_ID, OPE4.OPE_NO, OPE4.OPE_PASS_COUNT, OPE4.HOLD_REASON_CODE||': '||OPE4.HOLD_REASON_DESC AS HOLD_COMMENT FROM MMVIEW.FHOPEHS OPE4, T3 WHERE OPE4.LOT_ID=T3.LOT_ID AND OPE4.OPE_CATEGORY='LotHold' AND OPE4.MAINPD_ID=T3.MAINPD_ID AND OPE4.OPE_NO=T3.OPE_NO AND OPE4.OPE_PASS_COUNT=T3.OPE_PASS_COUNT) TEMP WHERE ROW_COL=1 ) SELECT T3.LOT_ID,T3.MAINPD_ID,T3.LOT_TYPE, T3.CUR_WAFER_QTY, T3.MODPD_IDENT, T3.OPE_NO, T3.PD_NAME, T3.DEPARTMENT, T3.EQP_TYPE, T3.CT_HRS, T3.OPESTART_TIME, T3.OPEOUT_TIME, T4.HOLD_COMMENT, 0 AS AGRESSIVE FROM T3 LEFT JOIN T4 ON T4.MAINPD_ID=T3.MAINPD_ID AND T4.OPE_NO=T3.OPE_NO AND T4.OPE_PASS_COUNT=T3.OPE_PASS_COUNT ORDER BY OPESTART_TIME ;

SELECT A.*,B.OPE_NO, B.STD_CYCLE_TIME,B.CT_HRS FROM (SELECT PROD.MAINPD_ID, PF.D_THESYSTEMKEY, LOT.CREATED_TIME, LOT_ID, CURRENT_TIMESTAMP AS CURRENT_TIME FROM MMVIEW.FRLOT LOT , MMVIEW.FRPRODSPEC PROD , MMVIEW.FRPD PD , MMVIEW.FRPF PF WHERE LOT.PRODSPEC_OBJ=PROD.PRODSPEC_OBJ AND PROD.MAINPD_OBJ=PD.PD_OBJ AND PD.ACTIVE_MAINPF_OBJ=PF.PF_OBJ AND PF.PD_LEVEL='Main_Mod') A LEFT JOIN (SELECT PDLIST.D_KEY||'.'||POSLIST.D_KEY AS OPE_NO, PD2.STD_CYCLE_TIME, DECIMAL(PD2.STD_CYCLE_TIME/60 ,10,2) AS CT_HRS, '' AS AGRRESSIVETIME, PDLIST.D_THESYSTEMKEY FROM MMVIEW.FRPF_PDLIST PDLIST, MMVIEW.FRPD PD1, MMVIEW.FRPF PF, MMVIEW.FRPF_POSLIST POSLIST, MMVIEW.FRPOS POS, MMVIEW.FRPD PD2 WHERE PDLIST.PD_OBJ=PD1.PD_OBJ AND PD1.ACTIVE_PF_OBJ=PF.PF_OBJ AND PF.D_THESYSTEMKEY=POSLIST.D_THESYSTEMKEY AND POSLIST.POS_OBJ=POS.POS_OBJ AND POS.PD_OBJ=PD2.PD_OBJ ORDER BY OPE_NO) B ON A.D_THESYSTEMKEY=B.D_THESYSTEMKEY

dbQuery.sql: SELECT B.LOT_ID,A.* FROM (SELECT PDLIST.PD_ID AS MODULEPD_ID, PDLIST.D_KEY||'.'||POSLIST.D_KEY AS OPE_NO, PD2.PD_ID, PD2.PD_NAME AS OPE_NAME, CODE.DESCRIPTION AS DEPARTMENT, current_timestamp as Current_Time, decimal(PD2.STD_CYCLE_TIME/60,10,2) AS CT_HRS, PD2.RECIPE_OBJ, PD2.D_THESYSTEMKEY as FRPD_D_THESYSTEMKEY, PDLIST.D_THESYSTEMKEY as FRPF_PDLIST_THESYSTEMKEY FROM MMVIEW.FRPF_PDLIST PDLIST, MMVIEW.FRPD PD1, MMVIEW.FRPF PF, MMVIEW.FRPF_POSLIST POSLIST, MMVIEW.FRPOS POS, MMVIEW.FRPD PD2, MMVIEW.FRCODE CODE WHERE PDLIST.PD_OBJ=PD1.PD_OBJ AND PD1.ACTIVE_PF_OBJ=PF.PF_OBJ AND PF.D_THESYSTEMKEY=POSLIST.D_THESYSTEMKEY AND POSLIST.POS_OBJ=POS.POS_OBJ AND POS.PD_OBJ=PD2.PD_OBJ AND PD2.DEPARTMENT=CODE.CODE_ID AND CODE.CATEGORY_ID='Department') A, (SELECT LOT.OPE_NO, PF.D_THESYSTEMKEY,LOT.LOT_ID FROM MMVIEW.FRLOT LOT, MMVIEW.FRPF PF WHERE LOT.MAINPD_ID =PF.MAINPD_ID AND PF.PD_LEVEL='Main_Mod') B WHERE A.FRPF_PDLIST_THESYSTEMKEY=B.D_THESYSTEMKEY AND A.OPE_NO>B.OPE_NO ORDER BY A.OPE_NO

SELECT T1.LCRECIPE_OBJ, LISTAGG(T1.EQP_TYPE,'|') AS EQP_TYPE FROM (SELECT DISTINCT LRCP.LCRECIPE_OBJ,EQP.EQP_TYPE FROM MMVIEW.FRLRCP LRCP, MMVIEW.FRLRCP_DSET SET, MMVIEW.FRMRCP MRCP, MMVIEW.FRMRCP_EQP MRCP_EQP,MMVIEW.FREQP EQP WHERE LRCP.D_THESYSTEMKEY=SET.D_THESYSTEMKEY AND SET.RECIPE_OBJ=MRCP.RECIPE_OBJ AND MRCP.D_THESYSTEMKEY=MRCP_EQP.D_THESYSTEMKEY AND MRCP_EQP.EQP_OBJ=EQP.EQP_OBJ AND EQP.EQP_TYPE <> '' ORDER BY LCRECIPE_OBJ) T1 GROUP BY T1.LCRECIPE_OBJ

FROM MMVIEW.FRLOT LOT, MMVIEW.FRLOTPO LOTPO, SMVIEW.FBMNPD_PO MNPO, SMVIEW.FBPD PD, SMVIEW.FBDEPT DEPT
WHERE LOT.LOT_ID=LOTPO.LOT_ID AND LOT.MAINPD_ID=MNPO.D_THESYSTEMKEY AND LOT.OPE_NO=MNPO.OPER_NO AND MNPO.PD_IDENT =PD.D_THESYSTEMKEY AND PD.DEPT_OBJREF=DEPT.D_STRINGOBJREF
SELECT EQP_TYPE,EQP_ID FROM MMVIEW.FREQP

SELECT CASE WHEN T4.RECIPE_ID IS NOT NULL THEN CONCAT(T3.RECIPE_ID,'*') ELSE T3.RECIPE_ID END AS RECIPE_ID,T3.D_THESYSTEMKEY FROM (select T2.RECIPE_ID,T2.D_THESYSTEMKEY FROM (SELECT ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY T1.D_THESYSTEMKEY ORDER BY T1.RECIPE_ID) AS ROW_COL,T1.RECIPE_ID,T1.D_THESYSTEMKEY FROM (SELECT DISTINCT SET.RECIPE_ID,LRCP.D_THESYSTEMKEY FROM MMVIEW.FRLRCP LRCP, MMVIEW.FRLRCP_SSET SET, MMVIEW.FREQP EQP WHERE LRCP.D_THESYSTEMKEY=SET.D_THESYSTEMKEY AND EQP.EQP_OBJ=SET.EQP_OBJ ORDER BY LRCP.D_THESYSTEMKEY,SET.RECIPE_ID) T1 ORDER BY T1.D_THESYSTEMKEY ) T2 WHERE ROW_COL=1) T3 LEFT JOIN (select T2.RECIPE_ID,T2.D_THESYSTEMKEY FROM (SELECT ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY T1.D_THESYSTEMKEY ORDER BY T1.RECIPE_ID) AS ROW_COL,T1.RECIPE_ID,T1.D_THESYSTEMKEY FROM (SELECT DISTINCT SET.RECIPE_ID,LRCP.D_THESYSTEMKEY FROM MMVIEW.FRLRCP LRCP, MMVIEW.FRLRCP_SSET SET, MMVIEW.FREQP EQP WHERE LRCP.D_THESYSTEMKEY=SET.D_THESYSTEMKEY AND EQP.EQP_OBJ=SET.EQP_OBJ ORDER BY LRCP.D_THESYSTEMKEY,SET.RECIPE_ID) T1 ORDER BY T1.D_THESYSTEMKEY ) T2 WHERE ROW_COL=2) T4 ON T3.D_THESYSTEMKEY=T4.D_THESYSTEMKEY

SELECT CASE WHEN T4.EQP_TYPE IS NOT NULL THEN CONCAT(T3.EQP_TYPE,'*') ELSE T3.EQP_TYPE END AS EQP_TYPE,T3.D_THESYSTEMKEY FROM (select T2.EQP_TYPE,T2.D_THESYSTEMKEY FROM (SELECT ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY T1.D_THESYSTEMKEY ORDER BY T1.EQP_TYPE) AS ROW_COL,T1.EQP_TYPE,T1.D_THESYSTEMKEY FROM (SELECT DISTINCT EQP.EQP_TYPE,LRCP.D_THESYSTEMKEY FROM MMVIEW.FRLRCP LRCP, MMVIEW.FRLRCP_SSET SET, MMVIEW.FREQP EQP WHERE LRCP.D_THESYSTEMKEY=SET.D_THESYSTEMKEY AND EQP.EQP_OBJ=SET.EQP_OBJ ORDER BY LRCP.D_THESYSTEMKEY,EQP.EQP_TYPE) T1 ORDER BY T1.D_THESYSTEMKEY ) T2 WHERE ROW_COL=1) T3 LEFT JOIN (select T2.EQP_TYPE,T2.D_THESYSTEMKEY FROM (SELECT ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY T1.D_THESYSTEMKEY ORDER BY T1.EQP_TYPE) AS ROW_COL,T1.EQP_TYPE,T1.D_THESYSTEMKEY FROM (SELECT DISTINCT EQP.EQP_TYPE,LRCP.D_THESYSTEMKEY FROM MMVIEW.FRLRCP LRCP, MMVIEW.FRLRCP_SSET SET, MMVIEW.FREQP EQP WHERE LRCP.D_THESYSTEMKEY=SET.D_THESYSTEMKEY AND EQP.EQP_OBJ=SET.EQP_OBJ ORDER BY LRCP.D_THESYSTEMKEY,EQP.EQP_TYPE) T1 ORDER BY T1.D_THESYSTEMKEY ) T2 WHERE ROW_COL=2) T4 ON T3.D_THESYSTEMKEY=T4.D_THESYSTEMKEY

SELECT T1.D_THESYSTEMKEY,LISTAGG(T1.EQP_ID,'|') AS EQP_ID FROM (SELECT DISTINCT EQP.EQP_ID,LRCP.D_THESYSTEMKEY FROM MMVIEW.FRLRCP LRCP, MMVIEW.FRLRCP_SSET SET, MMVIEW.FREQP EQP WHERE LRCP.D_THESYSTEMKEY=SET.D_THESYSTEMKEY AND EQP.EQP_OBJ=SET.EQP_OBJ ORDER BY LRCP.D_THESYSTEMKEY,EQP.EQP_ID) T1 GROUP BY T1.D_THESYSTEMKEY

SELECT CASE WHEN T4.RECIPE_ID IS NOT NULL THEN CONCAT(T3.RECIPE_ID,'*') ELSE T3.RECIPE_ID END AS RECIPE_ID,T3.D_THESYSTEMKEY FROM (select T2.RECIPE_ID,T2.D_THESYSTEMKEY FROM (SELECT ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY T1.D_THESYSTEMKEY ORDER BY T1.RECIPE_ID) AS ROW_COL,T1.RECIPE_ID,T1.D_THESYSTEMKEY FROM (SELECT DISTINCT SET.RECIPE_ID, LRCP.D_THESYSTEMKEY FROM MMVIEW.FRLRCP LRCP, MMVIEW.FRLRCP_DSET SET, MMVIEW.FRMRCP MRCP, MMVIEW.FRMRCP_EQP MRCP_EQP, MMVIEW.FREQP EQP WHERE SET.D_THESYSTEMKEY=LRCP.D_THESYSTEMKEY AND MRCP.RECIPE_OBJ=SET.RECIPE_OBJ AND MRCP_EQP.D_THESYSTEMKEY=MRCP.D_THESYSTEMKEY AND EQP.EQP_OBJ=MRCP_EQP.EQP_OBJ ORDER BY LRCP.D_THESYSTEMKEY, SET.RECIPE_ID) T1 ORDER BY T1.D_THESYSTEMKEY ) T2 WHERE ROW_COL=1) T3 LEFT JOIN (select T2.RECIPE_ID,T2.D_THESYSTEMKEY FROM (SELECT ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY T1.D_THESYSTEMKEY ORDER BY T1.RECIPE_ID) AS ROW_COL,T1.RECIPE_ID,T1.D_THESYSTEMKEY FROM (SELECT DISTINCT SET.RECIPE_ID, LRCP.D_THESYSTEMKEY FROM MMVIEW.FRLRCP LRCP, MMVIEW.FRLRCP_DSET SET, MMVIEW.FRMRCP MRCP, MMVIEW.FRMRCP_EQP MRCP_EQP, MMVIEW.FREQP EQP WHERE SET.D_THESYSTEMKEY=LRCP.D_THESYSTEMKEY AND MRCP.RECIPE_OBJ=SET.RECIPE_OBJ AND MRCP_EQP.D_THESYSTEMKEY=MRCP.D_THESYSTEMKEY AND EQP.EQP_OBJ=MRCP_EQP.EQP_OBJ ORDER BY LRCP.D_THESYSTEMKEY, SET.RECIPE_ID) T1 ORDER BY T1.D_THESYSTEMKEY ) T2 WHERE ROW_COL=2) T4 ON T3.D_THESYSTEMKEY=T4.D_THESYSTEMKEY

SELECT CASE WHEN T4.EQP_TYPE IS NOT NULL THEN CONCAT(T3.EQP_TYPE,'*') ELSE T3.EQP_TYPE END AS EQP_TYPE,T3.D_THESYSTEMKEY FROM (select T2.EQP_TYPE,T2.D_THESYSTEMKEY FROM (SELECT ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY T1.D_THESYSTEMKEY ORDER BY T1.EQP_TYPE) AS ROW_COL,T1.EQP_TYPE,T1.D_THESYSTEMKEY FROM (SELECT DISTINCT EQP.EQP_TYPE, LRCP.D_THESYSTEMKEY FROM MMVIEW.FRLRCP LRCP, MMVIEW.FRLRCP_DSET SET, MMVIEW.FRMRCP MRCP, MMVIEW.FRMRCP_EQP MRCP_EQP, MMVIEW.FREQP EQP WHERE SET.D_THESYSTEMKEY=LRCP.D_THESYSTEMKEY AND MRCP.RECIPE_OBJ=SET.RECIPE_OBJ AND MRCP_EQP.D_THESYSTEMKEY=MRCP.D_THESYSTEMKEY AND EQP.EQP_OBJ=MRCP_EQP.EQP_OBJ AND EQP.EQP_TYPE <>'' ORDER BY LRCP.D_THESYSTEMKEY, EQP.EQP_TYPE) T1 ORDER BY T1.D_THESYSTEMKEY ) T2 WHERE ROW_COL=1) T3 LEFT JOIN (select T2.EQP_TYPE,T2.D_THESYSTEMKEY FROM (SELECT ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY T1.D_THESYSTEMKEY ORDER BY T1.EQP_TYPE) AS ROW_COL,T1.EQP_TYPE,T1.D_THESYSTEMKEY FROM (SELECT DISTINCT EQP.EQP_TYPE, LRCP.D_THESYSTEMKEY FROM MMVIEW.FRLRCP LRCP, MMVIEW.FRLRCP_DSET SET, MMVIEW.FRMRCP MRCP, MMVIEW.FRMRCP_EQP MRCP_EQP, MMVIEW.FREQP EQP WHERE SET.D_THESYSTEMKEY=LRCP.D_THESYSTEMKEY AND MRCP.RECIPE_OBJ=SET.RECIPE_OBJ AND MRCP_EQP.D_THESYSTEMKEY=MRCP.D_THESYSTEMKEY AND EQP.EQP_OBJ=MRCP_EQP.EQP_OBJ AND EQP.EQP_TYPE <>'' ORDER BY LRCP.D_THESYSTEMKEY, EQP.EQP_TYPE) T1 ORDER BY T1.D_THESYSTEMKEY ) T2 WHERE ROW_COL=2) T4 ON T3.D_THESYSTEMKEY=T4.D_THESYSTEMKEY

SELECT T1.D_THESYSTEMKEY,LISTAGG(T1.EQP_ID,'|') AS EQP_ID FROM (SELECT DISTINCT EQP.EQP_ID, LRCP.D_THESYSTEMKEY FROM MMVIEW.FRLRCP LRCP, MMVIEW.FRLRCP_DSET SET, MMVIEW.FRMRCP MRCP, MMVIEW.FRMRCP_EQP MRCP_EQP, MMVIEW.FREQP EQP WHERE SET.D_THESYSTEMKEY=LRCP.D_THESYSTEMKEY AND MRCP.RECIPE_OBJ=SET.RECIPE_OBJ AND MRCP_EQP.D_THESYSTEMKEY=MRCP.D_THESYSTEMKEY AND EQP.EQP_OBJ=MRCP_EQP.EQP_OBJ ORDER BY LRCP.D_THESYSTEMKEY, EQP.EQP_ID) T1 GROUP BY T1.D_THESYSTEMKEY

SELECT D_THESYSTEMKEY,NOTE_CONTENTS FROM (SELECT ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY B.D_THESYSTEMKEY ORDER BY A.D_KEY DESC ) AS ROW_COL, B.NOTE_CONTENTS, A.D_THESYSTEMKEY, A.D_KEY FROM MMVIEW.FRLOT_OPENOTE A, MMVIEW.FRLOTOPENOTE B WHERE A.NOTE_OBJ=B.NOTE_OBJ ) TEMP WHERE ROW_COL =1

SELECT * FROM (SELECT ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY D_THESYSTEMKEY) AS ROW_COL, HOLD_USER_ID, CASE WHEN D_THESYSTEMKEY IN (SELECT D_THESYSTEMKEY FROM MMVIEW.FRLOT_HOLDRECORD GROUP BY D_THESYSTEMKEY having count(D_THESYSTEMKEY) >1) THEN CONCAT(HOLD_REASON_ID,'*') ELSE HOLD_REASON_ID END HOLD_REASON_ID, D_THESYSTEMKEY, HOLD_TIME FROM MMVIEW.FRLOT_HOLDRECORD) A WHERE A.ROW_COL= 1 ORDER BY A.HOLD_TIME DESC

SELECT TEMP.LOT_ID, TEMP.NOTE_CONTENTS FROM (SELECT ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY B.LOT_ID ORDER BY A.D_KEY DESC ) AS ROW_COL, B.NOTE_CONTENTS, B.LOT_ID, A.D_KEY FROM MMVIEW.FRLOT_NOTE A, MMVIEW.FRLOTNOTE B WHERE A.NOTE_OBJ=B.NOTE_OBJ) TEMP WHERE ROW_COL =1
SELECT EQP_ID, E10_STATE, CUR_STATE_ID, '' AS CONVRT_STATE FROM MMVIEW.FREQP

SELECT EQP_ID, EQP_STATE, E10_STATE, NEW_EQP_STATE, '' AS CONVERT_STATE, START_TIME, END_TIME, ST.DESCRIPTION, END_TIME-START_TIME AS DURATION, CLAIM_USER_ID, CLAIM_MEMO, DATE(START_TIME) AS FAB_DATE FROM MMVIEW.FHESCHS, MMVIEW.FREQPST ST WHERE EQP_STATE<>NEW_EQP_STATE AND EQP_STATE=ST. EQPSTATE_ID ORDER BY EQP_ID, START_TIME

SELECT EQP_ID||'-'||PROCRSC_ID AS EQP_ID, PR_STATE AS EQP_STATE, E10_STATE, NEW_PR_STATE AS NEW_EQP_STATE, '' AS CONVERT_STATE, START_TIME, END_TIME, ST.DESCRIPTION, END_TIME-START_TIME AS DURATION, CLAIM_USER_ID, CLAIM_MEMO, DATE(START_TIME) AS FAB_DATE FROM MMVIEW.FHCSCHS , MMVIEW.FREQPST ST WHERE --EQP_ID IN (SELECT EQP_ID FROM FREQP WHERE ) PR_STATE<>NEW_PR_STATE AND PR_STATE=ST. EQPSTATE_ID ORDER BY EQP_ID, START_TIME

SELECT EQP_ID||'-'||PORT_ID AS EQP_ID, PORT_STATE AS EQP_STATE, '' AS E10_STATE, '' AS NEW_EQP_STATE, '' AS CONVERT_STATE, CLAIM_TIME AS START_TIME, '' AS END_TIME, '' AS DESCRIPTION, 0 AS DURATION, CLAIM_USER_ID, CLAIM_MEMO, DATE(CLAIM_TIME) AS FAB_DATE FROM MMVIEW.FHEQPPORTSCHS --WHERE --EQP_ID IN (SELECT EQP_ID FROM FREQP WHERE ) ORDER BY EQP_ID, START_TIME

--Current status SELECT SCHS.EQP_ID, SCHS.EQP_STATE, SCHS.E10_STATE, SCHS.NEW_EQP_STATE, '' AS CONVERT_STATE, to_char(timestamp(schs.start_time),'YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI:SS') as start_time, -- SCHS.START_TIME, to_char(timestamp(SCHS.END_TIME),'YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI:SS') as END_TIME, ST.DESCRIPTION, SCHS.END_TIME-SCHS.START_TIME AS DURATION, SCHS.CLAIM_USER_ID, SCHS.CLAIM_MEMO, '1' AS ITEM, DATE(SCHS.START_TIME) AS FAB_DATE, SUBSTR(EQP.EQP_TYPE, 1, 1) AS MODULE, EQP.EQP_TYPE, to_char(CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,'YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI:SS') AS CURRENT_TIME FROM MMVIEW.FREQP EQP, MMVIEW.FHESCHS SCHS, MMVIEW.FREQPST ST WHERE EQP.EQP_ID = SCHS.EQP_ID AND EQP_STATE = ST. EQPSTATE_ID AND SCHS.EQP_STATE= ST. EQPSTATE_ID UNION ALL SELECT SCHS.EQP_ID||'-'||SCHS.PROCRSC_ID AS EQP_ID, SCHS.PR_STATE AS EQP_STATE, SCHS.E10_STATE, SCHS.NEW_PR_STATE AS NEW_EQP_STATE, '' AS CONVERT_STATE, to_char(timestamp(schs.start_time),'YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI:SS') as start_time, -- SCHS.START_TIME, to_char(timestamp(SCHS.END_TIME),'YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI:SS') as END_TIME, --SCHS.START_TIME, --SCHS.END_TIME, ST.DESCRIPTION, SCHS.END_TIME- SCHS.START_TIME AS DURATION, SCHS.CLAIM_USER_ID, SCHS.CLAIM_MEMO, '2' AS ITEM, DATE(SCHS.START_TIME) AS FAB_DATE, SUBSTR(EQP.EQP_TYPE, 1, 1) AS MODULE, EQP.EQP_TYPE, to_char(CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,'YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI:SS') AS CURRENT_TIME FROM MMVIEW.FREQP EQP, MMVIEW.FHCSCHS SCHS, MMVIEW.FREQPST ST WHERE EQP.EQP_ID=SCHS.EQP_ID AND SCHS.PR_STATE=ST. EQPSTATE_ID UNION ALL SELECT SCHS.EQP_ID||'-'||PORT_ID AS EQP_ID, SCHS.PORT_STATE AS EQP_STATE, '' AS E10_STATE, '' AS NEW_EQP_STATE, '' AS CONVERT_STATE,
to_char(timestamp(SCHS.CLAIM_TIME),'YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI:SS') as start_time, NULL AS END_TIME, '' AS DESCRIPTION, 0 AS DURATION, '' AS CLAIM_USER_ID, SCHS.CLAIM_MEMO, '3' AS ITEM, DATE(SCHS.CLAIM_TIME) AS FAB_DATE, SUBSTR(EQP.EQP_TYPE, 1, 1) AS MODULE, EQP.EQP_TYPE, to_char(CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,'YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI:SS') AS CURRENT_TIME FROM MMVIEW.FREQP EQP, MMVIEW.FHEQPPORTSCHS SCHS WHERE EQP.EQP_ID=SCHS.EQP_ID ORDER BY START_TIME desc
SELECT CODE_ID AS MODULE FROM MMVIEW.FRCODE WHERE CATEGORY_ID='Department'
SELECT EQP_TYPE FROM MMVIEW.FREQP WHERE EQP_CATEGORY='Equipment Type'

SELECT EQP_ID, EQP_STATE, E10_STATE ,START_TIME, DECIMAL(DOUBLE(timestampdiff(4,char(end_time - start_time)))/60,10,2) AS Duration, CLAIM_USER_ID,CLAIM_MEMO, CURRENT_TIMESTAMP AS CURRENT_TIME FROM MMVIEW.FHESCHS ORDER BY EQP_ID , START_TIME

SELECT TEQP.DEPT AS DEP, TEQP.EQP_ID, TEQP.NAME AS EQP_NAME, TEQP.CLAIM_TIME, TEQP.STAY_HRS, W.WIP , T.CHG_COMMENT, TEQP.CUR_STATUS, TEQP.USER_ID, TEQP.D_THESYSTEMKEY, TEQP.TYPE, TEQP.CUR_STATE_ID AS STATE_ID, TEQP.E10_STATE_ID, TEQP.EQPSTATE_ID, CURRENT_TIMESTAMP AS CURRENT_TIME FROM ( SELECT C.CODE_ID||':'||C.DESCRIPTION AS DEPT, EQP.EQP_ID, EQP.EQP_NAME AS NAME, EQP.CUR_STATE_ID, ST.E10_STATE_ID, ST.EQPSTATE_ID, EQP.CLAIM_TIME, CASE WHEN EQP.CLAIM_TIME<'2018-04-01-00.00.00.000000' THEN -1 ELSE DECIMAL(DOUBLE(TIMESTAMPDIFF(4, CURRENT TIMESTAMP-EQP.CLAIM_TIME))/60, 6, 2) END AS STAY_HRS, 0 AS WIP_QTY, '' AS CHG_COMMENT, ST.EQPSTATE_NAME||':'||ST. DESCRIPTION AS CUR_STATUS, EQP.CLAIM_USER_ID AS USER_ID, EQP.D_THESYSTEMKEY, '1' AS TYPE FROM MMVIEW.FREQP EQP , MMVIEW.FRCODE C , MMVIEW.FREQPST ST WHERE EQP.E10_STATE NOT IN ('PRD', 'SBY') AND C.CODE_ID=SUBSTR(EQP.EQP_ID, 1, 1) AND C.CATEGORY_ID='Department' AND EQP.CUR_STATE_OBJ=ST.EQPSTATE_OBJ) TEQP LEFT JOIN ( SELECT E.EQP_ID, COUNT(E.EQP_ID) AS WIP FROM MMVIEW.FRLOT_EQP E, MMVIEW.FRLOT LOT WHERE LOT.D_THESYSTEMKEY=E.D_THESYSTEMKEY AND LOT.LOT_STATE='ACTIVE' AND LOT.LOT_FINISHED_STATE='' AND LOT.LOT_INV_STATE='OnFloor' GROUP BY E.EQP_ID) W ON W.EQP_ID=TEQP.EQP_ID LEFT JOIN ( SELECT * FROM ( SELECT ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY NOTE.D_THESYSTEMKEY ORDER BY NOTE.D_KEY) AS ROW_COL, EQPNOTE.NOTE_TITLE ||EQPNOTE.NOTE_CONTENTS AS CHG_COMMENT, NOTE.D_THESYSTEMKEY, NOTE.D_KEY FROM MMVIEW.FREQP_NOTE NOTE, MMVIEW.FREQPNOTE EQPNOTE WHERE NOTE.NOTE_OBJ=EQPNOTE.NOTE_OBJ) TEMP WHERE ROW_COL =1) T ON TEQP.D_THESYSTEMKEY=T.D_THESYSTEMKEY UNION SELECT C.CODE_ID||':'||C.DESCRIPTION AS DEP, RSC.EQP_ID||'-'||RSC.PROCRSC_ID AS EQP_ID, RSC.PROCRSC_NAME AS EQP_NAME, RSC.CLAIM_TIME, CASE WHEN RSC.CLAIM_TIME <'2018-04-01-00.00.00.000000' THEN -1 ELSE DECIMAL(DOUBLE(TIMESTAMPDIFF(4, CURRENT TIMESTAMP-RSC.CLAIM_TIME))/60, 6, 2) END AS STAY_HRS, NULL AS WIP, '' AS CHG_COMMENT, ST.EQPSTATE_NAME||':'||ST. DESCRIPTION AS CUR_STATUS, RSC.CLAIM_USER_ID AS USER_ID, RSC.D_THESYSTEMKEY, '2' AS TYPE, RSC.EQP_STATE_ID AS STATE_ID, ST.E10_STATE_ID, ST.EQPSTATE_ID, CURRENT_TIMESTAMP AS CURRENT_TIME FROM MMVIEW.FRPRCRSC RSC , MMVIEW.FREQP EQP , MMVIEW.FRCODE C , MMVIEW.FREQPST ST WHERE EQP.E10_STATE NOT IN ('PRD', 'SBY') AND RSC.EQP_ID=EQP.EQP_ID AND C.CODE_ID=SUBSTR(EQP.EQP_ID, 1, 1) AND C.CATEGORY_ID='Department' AND RSC.EQP_STATE_OBJ=ST.EQPSTATE_OBJ UNION SELECT C.CODE_ID||':'||C.DESCRIPTION AS DEP, PORT.EQP_ID||'-'||PORT.PORT_ID AS EQP_ID, PORT.PORT_NAME AS EQP_ID, PORT.CLAIM_TIME, CASE WHEN PORT.CLAIM_TIME <'2018-04-01-00.00.00.000000' THEN -1 ELSE DECIMAL(DOUBLE(TIMESTAMPDIFF(4, CURRENT TIMESTAMP-PORT.CLAIM_TIME))/60, 6, 2) END AS STAY_HRS, NULL AS WIP_QTY, '' AS CHG_COMMENT, PORT.E10_STATE ||':'||PORT.PORT_STATE AS CUR_STATUS, PORT.CLAIM_USER_ID AS USER_ID, EQP.D_THESYSTEMKEY, '3' AS TYPE, '0' AS STATE_ID, '' AS E10_STATE_ID, '' AS EQPSTATE_ID, CURRENT_TIMESTAMP AS CURRENT_TIME FROM MMVIEW.FRPORT PORT , MMVIEW.FREQP EQP , MMVIEW.FRCODE C WHERE EQP.E10_STATE NOT IN ('PRD', 'SBY') AND PORT.EQP_ID=EQP.EQP_ID AND C.CODE_ID=SUBSTR(EQP.EQP_ID, 1, 1) AND C.CATEGORY_ID='Department'

SELECT T3.EQP_ID , TOTAL_WIP , HOLD_WIP , EQP_NAME , AREA_ID , NONPROD_WIP , NONPROD_HOLD , CUR_STATUS , STAY_HRS , DEPARTMENT ,CURRENT_TIMESTAMP AS CURRENT_TIME FROM ( SELECT T2.EQP_ID, TOTAL_WIP, HOLD_WIP, EQP_NAME, AREA_ID, NONPROD_WIP, CUR_STATUS, STAY_HRS, DEPARTMENT FROM ( SELECT T1.EQP_ID, TOTAL_WIP, PROD_HOLD AS HOLD_WIP, EQP_NAME, AREA_ID, CUR_STATUS, STAY_HRS, DEPARTMENT FROM ( SELECT EQP.EQP_ID, PROD_WIP AS TOTAL_WIP, EQP_NAME, AREA_ID, CUR_STATUS, STAY_HRS, DEPARTMENT FROM ( SELECT EQP_ID, EQP_NAME, AREA_ID, EQP.CUR_STATE_ID||'-'||EQP.E10_STATE AS CUR_STATUS, CASE WHEN STATE_CHG_TIME<'2018-04-01-00.00.00.000000' THEN -1 ELSE DECIMAL(DOUBLE(TIMESTAMPDIFF(4, CURRENT TIMESTAMP-STATE_CHG_TIME))/60, 6,2) END AS STAY_HRS, SUBSTR(EQP_ID, 1, 1) AS DEPARTMENT FROM MMVIEW.FREQP EQP )EQP LEFT JOIN ( SELECT EQP_ID, SUM(WIP_QTY) AS PROD_WIP FROM ( SELECT LOTEQP.EQP_ID, LOT.LOT_TYPE, SUM(LOT.QTY) AS WIP_QTY FROM MMVIEW.FRLOT_EQP LOTEQP, MMVIEW.FRLOT LOT WHERE LOTEQP.D_THESYSTEMKEY=LOT.D_THESYSTEMKEY AND LOT.LOT_STATE='ACTIVE' AND LOT.LOT_FINISHED_STATE='' AND LOT.LOT_INV_STATE='OnFloor' GROUP BY LOTEQP.EQP_ID, LOT.LOT_TYPE )TWIP WHERE LOT_TYPE IN ('Production','Engineering') GROUP BY EQP_ID )TPROD_WIP ON EQP.EQP_ID=TPROD_WIP.EQP_ID )T1 LEFT JOIN ( SELECT EQP_ID, SUM(HOLD_QTY) AS PROD_HOLD FROM ( SELECT HOLDEQP.EQP_ID, LOT.LOT_TYPE, SUM(LOT.QTY) AS HOLD_QTY FROM MMVIEW.FRLOT_HOLDEQP HOLDEQP, MMVIEW.FRLOT LOT WHERE HOLDEQP.D_THESYSTEMKEY=LOT.D_THESYSTEMKEY AND LOT.LOT_STATE='ACTIVE' AND LOT.LOT_FINISHED_STATE='' AND LOT_HOLD_STATE='ONHOLD' AND LOT.LOT_INV_STATE='OnFloor' GROUP BY HOLDEQP.EQP_ID, LOT.LOT_TYPE )THOLD WHERE LOT_TYPE IN ('Production','Engineering') GROUP BY EQP_ID )TPROD_HOLD ON T1.EQP_ID=TPROD_HOLD.EQP_ID )T2 LEFT JOIN ( SELECT EQP_ID, SUM(WIP_QTY) AS NONPROD_WIP FROM ( SELECT LOTEQP.EQP_ID, LOT.LOT_TYPE, SUM(LOT.QTY) AS WIP_QTY FROM MMVIEW.FRLOT_EQP LOTEQP, MMVIEW.FRLOT LOT WHERE LOTEQP.D_THESYSTEMKEY=LOT.D_THESYSTEMKEY AND LOT.LOT_STATE='ACTIVE' AND LOT.LOT_FINISHED_STATE='' AND LOT.LOT_INV_STATE='OnFloor' GROUP BY LOTEQP.EQP_ID, LOT.LOT_TYPE )TWIP WHERE LOT_TYPE NOT IN ('Production','Engineering') GROUP BY EQP_ID )TNONPROD_WIP ON T2.EQP_ID=TNONPROD_WIP.EQP_ID )T3 LEFT JOIN ( SELECT EQP_ID, SUM(HOLD_QTY) AS NONPROD_HOLD FROM ( SELECT HOLDEQP.EQP_ID, LOT.LOT_TYPE, SUM(LOT.QTY) AS HOLD_QTY FROM MMVIEW.FRLOT_HOLDEQP HOLDEQP, MMVIEW.FRLOT LOT WHERE HOLDEQP.D_THESYSTEMKEY=LOT.D_THESYSTEMKEY AND LOT.LOT_STATE='ACTIVE' AND LOT.LOT_FINISHED_STATE='' AND LOT_HOLD_STATE='ONHOLD' AND LOT.LOT_INV_STATE='OnFloor' GROUP BY HOLDEQP.EQP_ID, LOT.LOT_TYPE )THOLD WHERE LOT_TYPE NOT IN ('Production','Engineering') GROUP BY EQP_ID )TNONPROD_HOLD ON T3.EQP_ID=TNONPROD_HOLD.EQP_ID ORDER BY EQP_ID

SELECT LOT.LOT_ID, PO.MODULEPD_ID AS MODULEPD_ID, LOT.PRIORITY_CLASS, LOT.QTY, EQP2.USED_RECIPE_ID AS RECIPE_ID,EQP2.EQP_TYPE, CASE WHEN LOT_INV_STATE = 'NonProBank' THEN CASE WHEN LOT_FINISHED_STATE IN ('SCRAPPED','EMPTIED') THEN LOT_FINISHED_STATE ELSE LOT_INV_STATE END ELSE CASE WHEN LOT_HOLD_STATE = 'ONHOLD' THEN CASE WHEN LOT_FINISHED_STATE IN ('SCRAPPED','EMPTIED') THEN LOT_FINISHED_STATE ELSE LOT_HOLD_STATE END ELSE CASE WHEN LOT_STATE IN ('LOTCREATED','RELEASED','SHIPPED') THEN LOT_STATE WHEN LOT_STATE = 'FINSIHED' THEN LOT_FINISHED_STATE WHEN LOT_STATE = 'ACTIVE' THEN LOT_PROCESS_STATE END END END AS LOT_STATUS, EQP.EQP_ID, NULL AS ENTRY_TIME, NULL AS STAY_HRS, NULL AS INUSER, LOT.MAINPD_ID, LOT.OPE_NO, LOT.CLAIM_TIME, CURRENT_TIMESTAMP AS CURRENT_TIME FROM MMVIEW.FRLOT LOT, MMVIEW.FRLOT_EQP EQP, MMVIEW.FRLOTPO PO, MMVIEW.FREQP EQP2, ( SELECT LOT.LOT_ID, EQP.EQP_TYPE FROM MMVIEW.FRLOT_EQP LOTEQP, MMVIEW.FRLOT LOT, MMVIEW.FREQP EQP WHERE LOTEQP.EQP_ID=EQP.EQP_ID AND LOTEQP.D_THESYSTEMKEY=LOT.D_THESYSTEMKEY AND LOT.LOT_FINISHED_STATE='' AND LOT.LOT_HOLD_STATE='NOTONHOLD' UNION SELECT LOT.LOT_ID, EQP.EQP_TYPE FROM MMVIEW.FRLOT_HOLDEQP LOTEQP, MMVIEW.FRLOT LOT, MMVIEW.FREQP EQP WHERE LOTEQP.EQP_ID=EQP.EQP_ID AND LOTEQP.D_THESYSTEMKEY=LOT.D_THESYSTEMKEY AND LOT.LOT_FINISHED_STATE='' AND LOT.LOT_HOLD_STATE='ONHOLD' )LOTLIST WHERE LOT.LOT_ID IN LOTLIST.LOT_ID AND EQP2.EQP_TYPE IN LOTLIST.EQP_TYPE AND LOT.D_THESYSTEMKEY=EQP.D_THESYSTEMKEY AND LOT.LOT_ID=PO.LOT_ID AND EQP.EQP_ID=EQP2.EQP_ID

SELECT * FROM (SELECT ROW_NUMBER() OVER (PARTITION BY LOT_ID,MAINPD_ID,OPE_NO ORDER BY CLAIM_TIME DESC) AS ROW_COL,LOT_ID,MAINPD_ID,OPE_NO,OPE_CATEGORY,MOVE_TYPE, CLAIM_TIME AS ENTRY_TIME, DECIMAL(DOUBLE(TIMESTAMPDIFF(4, CURRENT TIMESTAMP - CLAIM_TIME))/60, 6,2) AS STAY_HRS , CLAIM_USER_ID AS INUSER FROM MMVIEW.FHOPEHS) WHERE ( OPE_CATEGORY='OperationComplete' OR ( OPE_CATEGORY='LocateBackward' AND MOVE_TYPE='BackwardOperation' ) OR ( OPE_CATEGORY='LocateBackward' AND MOVE_TYPE='BackwardStage' ) OR ( OPE_CATEGORY='LocateForward' AND MOVE_TYPE='ForwardOperation' ) OR ( OPE_CATEGORY='LocateForward' AND MOVE_TYPE='ForwardStage' ) OR OPE_CATEGORY='STB' ) AND ROW_COL=1

relationship.expression: [物理层].[SQL2].[LOT_ID]=[物理层].[SQL3].[LOT_ID]AND[物理层].[SQL2].[MAINPD_ID]=[物理层].[SQL3].[MAINPD_ID]AND[物理层].[SQL2].[OPE_NO]=[物理层].[SQL3].[OPE_NO]AND[物理层].[SQL2].[CLAIM_TIME]>=[物理层].[SQL3].[ENTRY_TIME]

dbQuery.sql: SELECT a.MEAS_LOT_ID, a.MEAS_EQP_ID, a.MEAS_OPE_NO, a.MEAS_PD_ID, a.CLAIM_TIME, b.MEAS_DCDEF_ID, b.DCITEM_NAME, b.ITEM_TYPE, b.MEAS_TYPE, b.WAFER_ID, b.DCITEM_VALUE, b.SCRN_UPPER_LIMIT, b.SPEC_UPPER_LIMIT, b.CNTL_UPPER_LIMIT, b.CNTL_LOWER_LIMIT, b.SPEC_LOWER_LIMIT, b.SCRN_LOWER_LIMIT, CURRENT_TIMESTAMP AS CURRENT_TIME FROM MMVIEW.FHCDATAHS a JOIN MMVIEW.FHCDATAHS_DATA b ON a.MEAS_LOT_ID=b.MEAS_LOT_ID AND a.MEAS_MAINPD_ID = b.MEAS_MAINPD_ID AND a.MEAS_OPE_NO = b.MEAS_OPE_NO AND a.MEAS_PASS_COUNT = b.MEAS_PASS_COUNT AND a.CLAIM_TIME = b.CLAIM_TIME AND a.MEAS_DCDEF_ID = b.MEAS_DCDEF_ID

SELECT T1.EQP_ID, T1.LOT_ID, T1.CAST_ID, T1.PRODSPEC_ID, T1.LOT_TYPE, PO.MODPD_IDENT AS MODULEPD_ID, T1.OPE_NO, T1.PD_ID, T1.PD_NAME, T1.RECIPE_ID, T1.OPERATIONSTART_TIME, T1.OPERATIONCOMPLETE_TIME, T1.RUN_HRS, T1.IN_WAFER_COUNT, T1.OUT_WAFER_COUNT, T1.CTRL_JOB, T1.OPE_CATEGORY, T1.SUB_LOT_TYPE, CURRENT_TIMESTAMP AS CURRENT_TIME FROM (SELECT a.EQP_ID, a.LOT_ID, a.CAST_ID, a.PRODSPEC_ID, a.LOT_TYPE, a.SUB_LOT_TYPE, a.PD_ID, a.PD_NAME, a.RECIPE_ID, a.OPE_CATEGORY, a.CTRL_JOB, a.CLAIM_TIME AS OperationStart_time, b.CLAIM_TIME AS OperationComplete_time, CASE WHEN b.CLAIM_TiME IS NOT NULL THEN DECIMAL(DOUBLE(TIMESTAMPDIFF(4, b.CLAIM_TIME-a.CLAIM_TIME))/60, 7, 2) ELSE NULL END AS Run_Hrs, a.CUR_WAFER_QTY AS IN_wafer_count, b.CUR_WAFER_QTY AS OUT_wafer_count, a.MAINPD_ID, a. OPE_NO FROM MMVIEW.FHOPEHS a LEFT JOIN MMVIEW.FHOPEHS b ON a.CTRL_JOB=b.CTRL_JOB AND b.OPE_CATEGORY='OperationComplete' AND a.LOT_ID=b.LOT_ID WHERE a.OPE_CATEGORY IN ('OperationStart') ORDER BY a.EQP_ID, a.CLAIM_TIME, LOT_ID)T1, SMVIEW.FBMNPD_PO PO WHERE PO.D_THESYSTEMKEY=T1.MAINPD_ID AND PO.OPER_NO=T1.OPE_NO ORDER BY T1.EQP_ID, T1.OperationStart_time, T1.LOT_ID

FROM MMVIEW.FRLOT LOT, SMVIEW.FBMNPD_PO MNPO, SMVIEW.FBPD PD, SMVIEW.FBDEPT DEPT WHERE LOT.PRIORITY_CLASS in (1,2) AND LOT.LOT_STATE='ACTIVE' AND LOT.LOT_FINISHED_STATE='' AND LOT.MAINPD_ID=MNPO.D_THESYSTEMKEY AND LOT.OPE_NO=MNPO.OPER_NO AND MNPO.PD_IDENT =PD.D_THESYSTEMKEY AND PD.DEPT_OBJREF=DEPT.D_STRINGOBJREF

SELECT CAST_ID, EQP_ID AS PHY_LOCATION, TRANS_STATE AS PHY_STATUS, DRBLSUBSTATE_ID AS STATE, DRBL_STATE AS STATUS, U.VALUE AS RESP_OWNER, INTEGER(TIMES_USED) AS USE_CNT, COMISSIONED_DATE AS CREATE_TIME, CAST_CATEGORY AS CAST_TYPE, CAST_USED_CAPACITY AS QTY, CURRENT_TIMESTAMP AS CURRENT_TIME FROM MMVIEW.FRCAST C LEFT JOIN MMVIEW.FRCAST_UDATA U ON U.D_THESYSTEMKEY=C.D_THESYSTEMKEY AND U.NAME='S_CARRIER_OWNER'
ORDER BY CAST_ID

SELECT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP AS CURRENT_TIME, T1.* FROM( ( SELECT MAIN.PRODSPEC_ID AS PRODSPEC_ID , PD1.PD_ID AS FROM_PD , PD1.PD_NAME AS FRPM_PD_NAME , Q.OP_NO AS FROM_OPE_NO , PD2.PD_ID AS TO_PD , PD2.PD_NAME AS TO_PD_NAME , Q.TARGET_OP_NO AS TO_OPE_NO, PD2.DEPT_IDENT AS MODULE , DECIMAL(Q.EXPIRED_TIME/60000,8,2) AS TIME_LIMIT_MIN FROM MMVIEW.FVMAINPOS_QRESTDFLT_ACTION Q , SMVIEW.FBMNPD_PO PO1 , SMVIEW.FBPD PD1 , SMVIEW.FBMNPD_PO PO2 , SMVIEW.FBPD PD2, ( SELECT PF.MAINPD_ID, PROD.PRODSPEC_ID FROM MMVIEW.FRPRODSPEC PROD, MMVIEW.FRPD PD, MMVIEW.FRPF PF WHERE PROD.PRODSPEC_ID IN ( SELECT DISTINCT PRODSPEC_ID FROM MMVIEW.FRPRODSPEC ) AND PROD.MAINPD_OBJ=PD.PD_OBJ AND PD.ACTIVE_MAINPF_OBJ=PF.PF_OBJ AND PF.PD_LEVEL='Main_Mod' ) MAIN WHERE Q.MAINPD_ID=MAIN.MAINPD_ID AND PO1.D_THESYSTEMKEY=Q.MAINPD_ID AND PO1.OPER_NO=Q.OP_NO AND PO1.PD_IDENT=PD1.D_THESYSTEMKEY AND PO2.D_THESYSTEMKEY=Q.MAINPD_ID AND PO2.OPER_NO=Q.TARGET_OP_NO AND PO2.PD_IDENT=PD2.D_THESYSTEMKEY UNION SELECT MAIN.PRODSPEC_ID AS PRODSPEC_ID , PD1.PD_ID AS FROM_PD , PD1.PD_NAME AS FRPM_PD_NAME , Q.OP_NO AS FROM_OPE_NO , PD2.PD_ID AS TO_PD , PD2.PD_NAME AS TO_PD_NAME , Q.TARGET_OP_NO AS TO_OPE_NO, PD2.DEPT_IDENT AS MODULE , DECIMAL(Q.EXPIRED_TIME/60000,8,2) AS TIME_LIMIT_MIN FROM MMVIEW.FVMAINPOS_QTIMESET_ACTION Q , SMVIEW.FBMNPD_PO PO1 , SMVIEW.FBPD PD1 , SMVIEW.FBMNPD_PO PO2 , SMVIEW.FBPD PD2, ( SELECT PF.MAINPD_ID, PROD.PRODSPEC_ID FROM MMVIEW.FRPRODSPEC PROD, MMVIEW.FRPD PD, MMVIEW.FRPF PF WHERE PROD.PRODSPEC_ID IN ( SELECT DISTINCT PRODSPEC_ID FROM MMVIEW.FRPRODSPEC ) AND PROD.MAINPD_OBJ=PD.PD_OBJ AND PD.ACTIVE_MAINPF_OBJ=PF.PF_OBJ AND PF.PD_LEVEL='Main_Mod' ) MAIN WHERE Q.MAINPD_ID=MAIN.MAINPD_ID AND PO1.D_THESYSTEMKEY=Q.MAINPD_ID AND PO1.OPER_NO=Q.OP_NO AND PO1.PD_IDENT=PD1.D_THESYSTEMKEY AND PO2.D_THESYSTEMKEY=Q.MAINPD_ID AND PO2.OPER_NO=Q.TARGET_OP_NO AND PO2.PD_IDENT=PD2.D_THESYSTEMKEY ) ) T1 ORDER BY FROM_OPE_NO

SELECT CODE.CODE_ID||':'||CODE.DESCRIPTION AS DEPARTMENT , E.EQP_CATEGORY , E.EQP_ID , E.EQP_ID AS EQP_Chamber_Port --, E.ONLINE_MODE , PORT.PORT_ID , MODE.ONLINE_MODE , E.E10_STATE||'.'||E.CUR_STATE_ID AS CUR_STATUS , ST.DESCRIPTION , E.STATE_CHG_TIME , CASE WHEN E.STATE_CHG_TIME < '2018-04-01-00.00.00.000000' THEN -1 ELSE DECIMAL(DOUBLE(TIMESTAMPDIFF(4, CURRENT TIMESTAMP-E.STATE_CHG_TIME))/60, 5,1) END AS STAY_HRS , E.STATE_CHG_USER_ID , USER.USER_FULL_NAME , '' AS REMARKS /* filled 48bytes of blank string for this value */ FROM MMVIEW.FREQP E, MMVIEW.FRCODE CODE, MMVIEW.FREQPST ST, MMVIEW.FRUSER USER, MMVIEW.FRPORT PORT, MMVIEW.FROPEMODE MODE WHERE CODE.CODE_ID=SUBSTR(E.EQP_ID, 1, 1) AND CODE.CATEGORY_ID='Department' AND ST.EQPSTATE_ID=E.CUR_STATE_ID AND USER.USER_ID= E.STATE_CHG_USER_ID AND E.EQP_ID = PORT.EQP_ID AND MODE.OPEMODE_ID=PORT.MCOPEMODE_ID
UNION ALL SELECT CODE.CODE_ID||':'||CODE.DESCRIPTION AS DEPARTMENT , '' AS EQP_CATEGORY , E.EQP_ID , E.EQP_ID||'-'||E.PROCRSC_ID AS EQP_Chamber_Port --, '' AS ONLINE_MODE , PORT.PORT_ID , MODE.ONLINE_MODE , E.E10_STATE ||'.'||E.EQP_STATE_ID AS CUR_STATUS , ST.DESCRIPTION , E.STATE_CHG_TIME , CASE WHEN E.STATE_CHG_TIME < '2018-04-01-00.00.00.000000' THEN -1 ELSE DECIMAL(DOUBLE(TIMESTAMPDIFF(4, CURRENT TIMESTAMP-E.STATE_CHG_TIME))/60, 5,1) END AS STAY_HRS , E.STATE_CHG_USER_ID , USER.USER_FULL_NAME , '' AS REMARKS /* filled 48bytes of blank string for this value */ FROM MMVIEW.FRPRCRSC E, MMVIEW.FRCODE CODE, MMVIEW.FREQPST ST, MMVIEW.FRUSER USER, MMVIEW.FRPORT PORT, MMVIEW.FROPEMODE MODE WHERE CODE.CODE_ID=SUBSTR(E.EQP_ID, 1, 1) AND CODE.CATEGORY_ID='Department' AND ST.EQPSTATE_ID=E.EQP_STATE_ID AND USER.USER_ID= E.STATE_CHG_USER_ID AND E.EQP_ID = PORT.EQP_ID AND MODE.OPEMODE_ID=PORT.MCOPEMODE_ID UNION ALL SELECT CODE.CODE_ID||':'||CODE.DESCRIPTION AS DEPARTMENT , '' AS EQP_CATEGORY , E.EQP_ID , E.EQP_ID||'-'||E.PORT_ID AS EQP_Chamber_Port -- , '' AS ONLINE_MODE , PORT.PORT_ID , MODE.ONLINE_MODE , E.E10_STATE ||'.'||E.PORT_STATE AS CUR_STATUS , '' AS DESCRIPTION , E.STATE_CHG_TIME , CASE WHEN E.STATE_CHG_TIME < '2018-04-01-00.00.00.000000' THEN -1 ELSE DECIMAL(DOUBLE(TIMESTAMPDIFF(4, CURRENT TIMESTAMP-E.STATE_CHG_TIME))/60, 5,1) END AS STAY_HRS , E.STATE_CHG_USER_ID , USER.USER_FULL_NAME , '' AS REMARKS /* filled 48bytes of blank string for this value */ FROM MMVIEW.FRPORT E, MMVIEW.FRCODE CODE, MMVIEW.FRUSER USER, MMVIEW.FRPORT PORT, MMVIEW.FROPEMODE MODE WHERE CODE.CODE_ID=SUBSTR(E.EQP_ID, 1, 1) AND CODE.CATEGORY_ID='Department' AND USER.USER_ID= E.STATE_CHG_USER_ID AND E.EQP_ID = PORT.EQP_ID AND MODE.OPEMODE_ID=PORT.MCOPEMODE_ID ORDER BY EQP_ID

SELECT T2.CLAIM_TIME , T2.OPE_CATEGORY , T2.PRODSPEC_ID , T2.LOT_TYPE , T2.CUR_OPE_NO , T2.LOT_ID , T2.CAST_ID , T2.EQP_ID , T2.RECIPE_ID , T2.RETICLE_ID , T2.CUR_WAFER_QTY , M.MEAS_DCDEF_ID , T2.CLAIM_USER_ID , T2.USER_FULL_NAME , T2.REMARKS, CURRENT_TIMESTAMP AS CURRENT_TIME, T2.CUR_MAINPD_ID, T2.CUR_PASS_COUNT FROM ( SELECT T1.CLAIM_TIME , T1.OPE_CATEGORY , T1.PRODSPEC_ID , T1.LOT_TYPE , T1.CUR_OPE_NO , T1.LOT_ID , T1.CAST_ID , T1.EQP_ID , T1.RECIPE_ID , R.RETICLE_ID , T1.CUR_WAFER_QTY , T1.CLAIM_USER_ID , T1.USER_FULL_NAME , T1.REMARKS , T1.CUR_MAINPD_ID , T1.CUR_PASS_COUNT FROM ( SELECT O.CLAIM_TIME , O.OPE_CATEGORY , O.PRODSPEC_ID , O.LOT_TYPE , CASE OPE_CATEGORY WHEN 'OperationStart' THEN O.OPE_NO WHEN 'OperationStartCancel' THEN O.OPE_NO WHEN 'OperationComplete' THEN O.PREV_OPE_NO END CUR_OPE_NO , O.LOT_ID , O.CAST_ID , O.EQP_ID , O.RECIPE_ID , O.CUR_WAFER_QTY , O.CLAIM_USER_ID , U.USER_FULL_NAME , ' ' AS REMARKS /* 32bytes of blank string */ , CASE OPE_CATEGORY WHEN 'OperationStart' THEN O.MAINPD_ID WHEN 'OperationStartCancel' THEN O.OPE_NO WHEN 'OperationComplete' THEN O.PREV_MAINPD_ID END CUR_MAINPD_ID , CASE OPE_CATEGORY WHEN 'OperationStart' THEN O.OPE_PASS_COUNT WHEN 'OperationStartCancel' THEN O.OPE_PASS_COUNT WHEN 'OperationComplete' THEN O.PREV_PASS_COUNT END CUR_PASS_COUNT FROM MMVIEW.FHOPEHS O, MMVIEW.FRUSER U WHERE O.OPE_CATEGORY IN ('OperationStart', 'OperationComplete', 'OperationStartCancel') AND U.USER_ID=O.CLAIM_USER_ID) T1 LEFT JOIN MMVIEW.FHOPEHS_RETICLE R ON R.LOT_ID=T1.LOT_ID AND T1.OPE_CATEGORY='OperationStart' AND R.CLAIM_TIME=T1.CLAIM_TIME AND R.MAINPD_ID=T1.CUR_MAINPD_ID AND R.OPE_NO=T1.CUR_OPE_NO AND R.OPE_PASS_COUNT=T1.CUR_PASS_COUNT) T2 LEFT JOIN MMVIEW.FHCDATAHS M ON M.MEAS_LOT_ID=T2.LOT_ID AND T2.OPE_CATEGORY='OperationComplete' AND M.CLAIM_TIME=T2.CLAIM_TIME AND M.MEAS_MAINPD_ID=T2.CUR_MAINPD_ID AND M.MEAS_OPE_NO=T2.CUR_OPE_NO AND M.MEAS_PASS_COUNT=T2.CUR_PASS_COUNT --------- union with FHESCHS for EQP status history UNION ALL SELECT START_TIME AS CLAIM_TIME , E10_STATE||'.'||EQP_STATE AS OPE_CATEGOEY , '' AS PRODSPEC_ID , '' AS LOT_TYPE , '' AS CUR_OPE_NO , '' AS LOT_ID , '' AS CAST_ID , EQP_ID , '' AS RECIPE_ID , '' AS RETICLE_ID , 0 AS CUR_WAFER_QTY , '' AS MEAS_DCDEF_ID , CLAIM_USER_ID , U.USER_FULL_NAME , ' ' AS REMARKS, /* 32bytes of blank string */ CURRENT_TIMESTAMP AS CURRENT_TIME, '' AS CUR_MAINPD_ID, 0 AS CUR_PASS_COUNT FROM MMVIEW.FHESCHS E, MMVIEW.FRUSER U WHERE ( EQP_STATE NOT LIKE '1%' AND EQP_STATE NOT LIKE '2%' ) AND EQP_STATE <> NEW_EQP_STATE AND U.USER_ID=E.CLAIM_USER_ID ORDER BY 1

SELECT CODE.DESCRIPTION AS DEPT, C.CAST_ID, L.LOT_ID, L.PRODSPEC_ID, L.QTY, L.OPE_NO, L.OPE_NAME, C.DRBL_STATE, C.DRBLSUBSTATE_ID, INTEGER(C.TIMES_USED) AS TIME_USED, CASE WHEN L.LOT_INV_STATE = 'NonProBank' THEN CASE WHEN LOT_FINISHED_STATE IN ('SCRAPPED','EMPTIED') THEN LOT_FINISHED_STATE ELSE LOT_INV_STATE END ELSE CASE WHEN LOT_HOLD_STATE = 'ONHOLD' THEN CASE WHEN LOT_FINISHED_STATE IN ('SCRAPPED','EMPTIED') THEN LOT_FINISHED_STATE ELSE LOT_HOLD_STATE END ELSE CASE WHEN LOT_STATE IN ('LOTCREATED','RELEASED','SHIPPED') THEN LOT_STATE WHEN LOT_STATE = 'FINSIHED' THEN LOT_FINISHED_STATE WHEN LOT_STATE = 'ACTIVE' THEN LOT_PROCESS_STATE END END END AS LOT_STATUS, C.EQP_ID, C.TRANS_STATE, L.LOT_OWNER_ID, U.VALUE AS CAST_OWNER, USER.DEPARTMENT, L.LOT_TYPE FROM mmview.FRLOT L, mmview.FRLOT_MTRLCONTNRS MTRL, mmview.FRCAST C, mmview.FRCAST_UDATA U, mmview.FRUSER USER, mmview.FRCODE CODE WHERE L.LOT_TYPE NOT IN ('Production','Engineering','Vendor') AND MTRL.D_THESYSTEMKEY=L.D_THESYSTEMKEY AND U.D_THESYSTEMKEY=C.D_THESYSTEMKEY AND U.NAME='S_CARRIER_OWNER' AND USER.USER_ID=U.VALUE AND CODE.CODE_ID=USER.DEPARTMENT AND CODE.CATEGORY_ID='Department' and MTRL.MTRLCONTNR_ID=C.cast_id ORDER BY DEPT, C.CAST_ID, L.LOT_ID

SELECT A1.*,A2.LOT_ID,A2.LOT_STATUS,TIMESTAMPDIFF(8,CHAR(A1.CURRENT_TIME -TIMESTAMP(A1.CLAIM_TIME) )) AS DURATION FROM ( ( SELECT C.CAST_ID, C.CLAIM_TIME, C.EQP_ID AS PHY_LOCATION, C.TRANS_STATE AS PHY_STATUS, C.DRBLSUBSTATE_ID AS STATE, C.DRBL_STATE AS STATUS, U.VALUE AS RESP_OWNER, INTEGER(C.TIMES_USED) AS USE_CNT, C.COMISSIONED_DATE AS CREATE_TIME, C.CAST_CATEGORY AS CAST_TYPE, C.CAST_USED_CAPACITY AS QTY,-------estimate qty != 0 --> condition 'Empty Foup' USER.USER_ID, USER.USER_FULL_NAME, Code.CODE_ID||': '||Code.DESCRIPTION AS DEPARTMENT , CURRENT_TIMESTAMP AS CURRENT_TIME FROM MMVIEW.FRCAST C LEFT JOIN MMVIEW.FRCAST_UDATA U ON U.D_THESYSTEMKEY=C.D_THESYSTEMKEY AND U.NAME='S_CARRIER_OWNER' LEFT JOIN MMVIEW.FRUSER User ON U.VALUE = USER.USER_ID LEFT JOIN MMVIEW.FRCODE Code ON User.DEPARTMENT = Code.CODE_ID AND Code.CATEGORY_ID='Department' --where qty=0 ORDER BY C.CAST_ID )A1 LEFT JOIN ( SELECT BASE1.CAST_ID, BASE1.LOT_ID, BASE2.LOT_STATUS FROM ( ( SELECT CAST_ID,LOT_ID FROM ( SELECT * FROM ( SELECT C.CAST_ID, L.LOT_ID FROM MMVIEW.FRCAST C LEFT JOIN MMVIEW.FRCAST_LOT L ON C.D_THESYSTEMKEY = L.D_THESYSTEMKEY
)T1 WHERE T1.LOT_ID is NULL
UNION ALL
SELECT distinct A.CAST_ID, --LOT.LOT_ID, --NUM, CASE WHEN A.NUM = 1 THEN LOT_ID WHEN A.NUM > 1 THEN subStr(LOT.lot_id,1,INSTR(LOT.LOT_ID,'.'))||'00*' --LOT_ID END AS LOT_ID FROM ( SELECT C.CAST_ID, C.D_THESYSTEMKEY, count(c.cast_id) as num FROM MMVIEW.FRCAST C,MMVIEW.FRCAST_LOT L WHERE C.D_THESYSTEMKEY = L.D_THESYSTEMKEY group by c.cast_id,C.D_THESYSTEMKEY )A,MMVIEW.FRCAST_LOT lOT WHERE A.D_THESYSTEMKEY = LOT.D_THESYSTEMKEY ) )BASE1 LEFT JOIN ( SELECT LOT_ID, CASE WHEN LOT_INV_STATE = 'NonProBank' THEN CASE WHEN LOT_FINISHED_STATE IN ('SCRAPPED','EMPTIED') THEN LOT_FINISHED_STATE ELSE LOT_INV_STATE END ELSE CASE WHEN LOT_HOLD_STATE = 'ONHOLD' THEN CASE WHEN LOT_FINISHED_STATE IN ('SCRAPPED','EMPTIED') THEN LOT_FINISHED_STATE ELSE LOT_HOLD_STATE END ELSE CASE WHEN LOT_STATE IN ('LOTCREATED','RELEASED','SHIPPED') THEN LOT_STATE WHEN LOT_STATE = 'FINSIHED' THEN LOT_FINISHED_STATE WHEN LOT_STATE = 'ACTIVE' THEN LOT_PROCESS_STATE END END END AS LOT_STATUS--, --CLAIM_TIME FROM MMVIEW.FRLOT )BASE2 ON subStr(BASE1.LOT_ID,1,INSTR(BASE1.LOT_ID,'.'))||'00' = BASE2.LOT_ID ) )A2 ON A1.CAST_ID = A2.CAST_ID )

SELECT BASE.PRIORITY_CLASS AS PRIORITY, BASE.OPE_NO, BASE.DESC, BASE.PRODUCT, BASE.LOT_ID, BASE.LOT_TYPE, type.eqp_id, TYPE.EQP_TYPE, CAST.FOUP, CAST.STATUS, CAST.LOCATION, BASE.LOT_HOLD_STATE, CODE.HOLD_REASON_ID, CODE.HOLD_CLAIM_MEMO, BASE.QTY, BASE.STY, BASE.QUEUE, BASE.STATE_CHG_USER_ID AS CHG_USER_ID, BASE.CHG_USER_NAME, BASE.DEPARTMENT, current_timestamp as current_time -- TYPE.EQP_TYPE --BASE.pfx_obj FROM ( SELECT T1.* ,U.USER_FULL_NAME AS CHG_USER_NAME,U.DEPARTMENT FROM ( SELECT LOT.PRIORITY_CLASS, LOT.OPE_NO, M.DESCRIPTION AS DESC, LOT.PRODSPEC_ID AS PRODUCT, LOT.LOT_ID, LOT.LOT_TYPE, --LOT.pfx_obj, LOT.LOT_HOLD_STATE, LOT.QTY, LOT.STATE_CHG_USER_ID , LOT.D_THESYSTEMKEY , timestampdiff(8,char(current_timestamp - timestamp(LOT.QUEUED_TIME))) AS QUEUE, timestampdiff(8,char(current_timestamp - timestamp(LOT.CLAIM_TIME))) AS STY FROM MMVIEW.FRLOT LOT, MMVIEW.FRPD M WHERE LOT.LOT_STATE='ACTIVE' AND LOT.LOT_TYPE<>'Vendor' AND M.PD_ID=LOT.MAINPD_ID AND M.PD_LEVEL='Main' )T1 LEFT JOIN ( SELECT user.USER_FULL_NAME, user.USER_ID, Code.CODE_ID||':'||Code.DESCRIPTION AS DEPARTMENT FROM MMVIEW.FRUSER User, MMVIEW.FRCODE Code WHERE Code.CATEGORY_ID='Department' AND User.DEPARTMENT = Code.CODE_ID )U ON T1.STATE_CHG_USER_ID = U.USER_ID )BASE LEFT JOIN ( SELECT M.D_THESYSTEMKEY, M.MTRLCONTNR_ID AS FOUP, C.TRANS_STATE AS STATUS, C.EQP_ID AS LOCATION FROM MMVIEW.FRLOT_MTRLCONTNRS M, MMVIEW.FRCAST C WHERE C.CAST_OBJ=M.MTRLCONTNR_OBJ )CAST ON BASE.D_THESYSTEMKEY = CAST.D_THESYSTEMKEY
LEFT JOIN MMVIEW.FRLOT_HOLDRECORD CODE ON BASE.D_THESYSTEMKEY = CODE.D_THESYSTEMKEY LEFT JOIN ( ( SELECT E.EQP_ID,E.D_THESYSTEMKEY,EQP.EQP_TYPE FROM MMVIEW.FRLOT_EQP E LEFT JOIN MMVIEW.FREQP EQP ON E.EQP_ID = EQP.EQP_ID ) UNION ALL ( SELECT E.EQP_ID,E.D_THESYSTEMKEY,EQP.EQP_TYPE FROM MMVIEW.FRLOT L,MMVIEW.FRLOT_HOLDEQP E,MMVIEW.FREQP EQP WHERE E.D_THESYSTEMKEY = L.D_THESYSTEMKEY AND E.EQP_ID = EQP.EQP_ID ) )TYPE ON BASE.D_THESYSTEMKEY = TYPE.D_THESYSTEMKEY order by BASE.PRIORITY_CLASS asc,BASE.STY desc
/*
select lot_id,l.lot_hold_state,e.eqp_id from mmview.frlot l,mmview.frlot_holdeqp e where e.d_thesystemkey=l.d_thesystemkey and l.lot_id='AA000015.00' LOT_ID EQP_ID */

SELECT BASE.DURABLE_ID, BASE.LOT_ID, BASE.CLAIM_TIME1, BASE.WAFER, BASE.PHYSICAL_LOCATION, BASE.PHYSICAL_STATUS, BASE.STATE, BASE.FOUP_STATUS, BASE.FOUP_TYPE, BASE.CREATE_TIME, TIMESTAMPDIFF(16,CHAR(timestamp(BASE.CLAIM_TIME1) - timestamp(BASE.CREATE_TIME))) AS DURATION, --day to_char( CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,'YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI:SS') AS CURRENT_TIME FROM ( SELECT ROW_NUMBER()OVER (Partition by CH.DURABLE_ID,OPE1.LOT_ID,CH.CLAIM_TIME ORDER BY OPE1.CLAIM_TIME ) AS ROW1, CH.DURABLE_ID, OPE1.LOT_ID, to_char(timestamp( CH.CLAIM_TIME),'YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI:SS') AS CLAIM_TIME1, OPE1.CLAIM_TIME AS CLAIM_TIME2, OPE1.CUR_WAFER_QTY AS WAFER, CH.LOCATION AS PHYSICAL_LOCATION, CH.XFER_STATUS AS PHYSICAL_STATUS, CH.DRBLSUBSTATE_ID AS STATE, CH.DURABLE_STATUS AS FOUP_STATUS, CAST.CAST_CATEGORY AS FOUP_TYPE, to_char(timestamp( CAST.COMISSIONED_DATE),'YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI:SS') AS CREATE_TIME FROM MMVIEW.FHDRCHS CH LEFT JOIN MMVIEW.FRCAST CAST ON CH.DURABLE_ID = CAST.CAST_ID LEFT JOIN MMVIEW.FHOPEHS OPE1 ON CH.DURABLE_ID = OPE1.CAST_ID AND CH.CLAIM_TIME < OPE1.CLAIM_TIME AND DATE(OPE1.CLAIM_TIME)>=DATE(CH.CLAIM_TIME)-3 DAYS ORDER BY CH.DURABLE_ID asc,CH.CLAIM_TIME DESC )BASE WHERE BASE.ROW1=1

SELECT W.LOT_ID, W.LOT_STATUS AS LOT_STATE, W.TRANS_STATE AS STATUS, W.CAST_ID AS FOUP, W.EQP_ID AS LOCATION, W.PRIORITY_CLASS AS PRIORITY, W.LOT_TYPE, W.QTY, W.OPE_NO, W.PD_DESC AS DESCRIPTION, W.EQP_TYPE, W.QUEUED_TIME AS ENTRY_TIME, W.HOLD_TIME, W.HOLD_REASON_ID, W.HOLD_CLAIM_MEMO, W.LOT_HOLD_STATE, W.STATE_CHG_USER_ID AS USER_ID, W.STATE_CHG_TIME, U.DEPARTMENT, U.USER_FULL_NAME, W.PRODSPEC_ID,
DECIMAL(DOUBLE(TIMESTAMPDIFF(4, CURRENT TIMESTAMP - W.STATE_CHG_TIME))/60, 5,1) as STATUS_HR, DECIMAL(DOUBLE(TIMESTAMPDIFF(4, CURRENT TIMESTAMP - W.QUEUED_TIME))/60, 5,1) as STAY_HR, DECIMAL(DOUBLE(TIMESTAMPDIFF(4, CURRENT TIMESTAMP - W.HOLD_TIME))/60, 5,1) as HOLD_HR FROM MMVIEW.RPTV_WIP_STATUS W LEFT JOIN ( SELECT user.USER_FULL_NAME, user.USER_ID, Code.CODE_ID||':'||Code.DESCRIPTION AS DEPARTMENT FROM MMVIEW.FRUSER User, MMVIEW.FRCODE Code WHERE Code.CATEGORY_ID='Department' AND User.DEPARTMENT = Code.CODE_ID )U ON STATE_CHG_USER_ID = U.USER_ID order by STAY_HR desc

SELECT W.LOT_ID, W.LOT_STATUS AS LOT_STATE, W.TRANS_STATE AS STATUS, W.CAST_ID AS FOUP, W.EQP_ID AS LOCATION, W.PRIORITY_CLASS AS PRIORITY, W.LOT_TYPE, W.QTY, W.OPE_NO, W.PD_DESC AS DESCRIPTION, W.EQP_TYPE, W.QUEUED_TIME AS ENTRY_TIME, W.HOLD_TIME, W.HOLD_REASON_ID, W.HOLD_CLAIM_MEMO, W.LOT_HOLD_STATE, W.STATE_CHG_USER_ID AS USER_ID, W.STATE_CHG_TIME, U.DEPARTMENT, U.USER_FULL_NAME, W.PRODSPEC_ID, DECIMAL(DOUBLE(TIMESTAMPDIFF(4, CURRENT TIMESTAMP - W.STATE_CHG_TIME))/60, 5,1) as STATUS_HR, DECIMAL(DOUBLE(TIMESTAMPDIFF(4, CURRENT TIMESTAMP - W.QUEUED_TIME))/60, 5,1) as STAY_HR, DECIMAL(DOUBLE(TIMESTAMPDIFF(4, CURRENT TIMESTAMP - W.HOLD_TIME))/60, 5,1) as HOLD_HR FROM MMVIEW.RPTV_WIP_STATUS W LEFT JOIN ( SELECT user.USER_FULL_NAME, user.USER_ID, Code.CODE_ID||':'||Code.DESCRIPTION AS DEPARTMENT FROM MMVIEW.FRUSER User, MMVIEW.FRCODE Code WHERE Code.CATEGORY_ID='Department' AND User.DEPARTMENT = Code.CODE_ID )U ON STATE_CHG_USER_ID = U.USER_ID WHERE LOT_HOLD_STATE ='ONHOLD' ORDER BY HOLD_HR DESC

select l.*,h.hold_reason_id from ( select d_thesystemkey, lot.Lot_ID,lot.Lot_Finished_State,lot.Bank_ID, lot.Lot_Type ,wafer.qty from mmview.frlot Lot left join ( select count(*) as qty,lot_obj from mmview.frwafer group by lot_obj ) wafer
on lot.lot_obj=wafer.lot_obj ) l left join mmview.frlot_holdrecord h on l.d_thesystemkey=h.d_thesystemkey

SELECT PRODUCT,WIP.EQP_TYPE,WIP,WIPPERLAYER,START_TIME,MOVEQTY,YSTMOVE,PRODUCT||' , '||WIP.EQP_TYPE AS LIK FROM (SELECT PRODUCT,EQP_TYPE,WIP,WIPPERLAYER FROM ISTRPT.REPORT005_WIP)WIP LEFT JOIN ( SELECT MOVE.PRODUCT_ID, MOVE.START_TIME, MOVE.DATE, MOVE.EQP_TYPE, MOVE.MOVEQTY, YMOVE.YSTMOVE FROM ISTRPT.RPT005_MOVE MOVE LEFT JOIN ( SELECT PRODUCT_ID, START_TIME, EQP_TYPE, MOVEQTY AS YSTMOVE FROM ISTRPT.RPT005_MOVE YMove WHERE YMove.DATE = CURRENT DATE - 1 DAYS )YMOVE ON MOVE.PRODUCT_ID = YMOVE.PRODUCT_ID AND MOVE.START_TIME = YMOVE.START_TIME AND MOVE.EQP_TYPE = YMOVE.EQP_TYPE )MOVE ON WIP.PRODUCT = MOVE.PRODUCT_ID AND WIP.EQP_TYPE = MOVE.EQP_TYPE ORDER BY WIP,WIPPERLAYER DESC

SELECT ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY ROW) AS ROWNO, PRODUCT,WIP.EQP_TYPE,WIP,WIPPERLAYER,ROW,START_TIME,MOVEQTY,YSTMOVE,PRODUCT||' , '||WIP.EQP_TYPE AS LIK FROM (SELECT PRODUCT,EQP_TYPE,WIP,WIPPERLAYER, 'ROW' AS ROW FROM ISTRPT.REPORT005_WIP)WIP LEFT JOIN ( SELECT MOVE.PRODUCT_ID, MOVE.START_TIME, MOVE.DATE, MOVE.EQP_TYPE, MOVE.MOVEQTY, YMOVE.YSTMOVE FROM ISTRPT.RPT005_MOVE MOVE LEFT JOIN ( SELECT PRODUCT_ID, START_TIME, EQP_TYPE, MOVEQTY AS YSTMOVE FROM ISTRPT.RPT005_MOVE YMove WHERE YMove.DATE = CURRENT DATE - 1 DAYS )YMOVE ON MOVE.PRODUCT_ID = YMOVE.PRODUCT_ID AND MOVE.START_TIME = YMOVE.START_TIME AND MOVE.EQP_TYPE = YMOVE.EQP_TYPE )MOVE ON WIP.PRODUCT = MOVE.PRODUCT_ID AND WIP.EQP_TYPE = MOVE.EQP_TYPE ORDER BY WIP,WIPPERLAYER DESC

SELECT OPEHS.LOT_ID, OPEHS.PRODSPEC_ID, OPEHS.CAST_ID AS FOUP_ID, OPEHS.CLAIM_CNTL_QTY AS QTY, OPEHS.PRIORITY_CLASS AS PRIORITY, OPEHS.MAINPD_ID AS ROUTE_ID, OPEHS.PD_ID AS OPE_ID, OPEHS.OPE_NO , OPEHS.PD_NAME AS OPE_NAME, OPEHS.EQP_ID, WCPHS.PROCRSC_ID AS CHAMBE_ID, EQP.EQP_TYPE, OPEHS.RECIPE_ID, OPEHS.OPE_CATEGORY, OPEHS.CLAIM_TIME AS OPE_TIME, CASE OPEH2.CLAIM_TIME WHEN NULL THEN '' ELSE timestampdiff(2,char(timestamp(OPEHS.CLAIM_TIME) - timestamp(OPEH2.CLAIM_TIME))) --Second END AS DURATION, OPEHS.REASON_CODE, OPEHS.REASON_DESCRIPTION, OPEHS.CLAIM_MEMO, OPEHS.CLAIM_USER_ID AS USER_ID, USER.USER_FULL_NAME, User.DESCRIPTION AS USER_DEPARTMENT, CURRENT_TIMESTAMP AS CURRENT_TIME FROM MMVIEW.FHOPEHS OPEHS LEFT JOIN MMVIEW.FREQP EQP ON OPEHS.EQP_ID = EQP.EQP_ID LEFT JOIN ( SELECT USER.USER_ID, USER.USER_FULL_NAME, CODE.DESCRIPTION FROM MMVIEW.FRUSER USER,MMVIEW.FRCODE CODE WHERE USER.DEPARTMENT = CODE.CODE_ID )USER ON OPEHS.CLAIM_USER_ID = USER.USER_ID LEFT JOIN MMVIEW.FHOPEHS OPEH2 ON OPEHS.LOT_ID = OPEH2.LOT_ID AND OPEHS.PREV_MAINPD_ID = OPEH2.MAINPD_ID AND OPEHS.PREV_OPE_NO = OPEH2.OPE_NO AND OPEHS.PREV_PD_ID = OPEH2.PD_ID AND OPEHS.PREV_PASS_COUNT = OPEH2.OPE_PASS_COUNT AND OPEH2.OPE_CATEGORY='OperationStart' AND OPEHS.OPE_CATEGORY='OperationComplete' LEFT JOIN MMVIEW.FHWCPHS WCPHS ON OPEHS.LOT_ID = WCPHS.LOT_ID AND OPEHS.MAINPD_ID = WCPHS.MAINPD_ID AND OPEHS.OPE_NO = WCPHS.OPE_NO AND OPEHS.OPE_PASS_COUNT = WCPHS.OPE_PASS_COUNT AND OPEHS.EQP_ID = WCPHS.EQP_ID AND OPEHS.CLAIM_TIME = WCPHS.CLAIM_TIME
